tionist to the hygienist and dentist, I could tell that the people working there were happy to be there. They were all so kind, friendly and knowledgeable. I clicked immediately with my hygienist, Colleen, and Dr. Kelly was amazing. She really took the time to review my dental history, talk through her recommendations, make sure I was comfortable with everything that was discussed, and included me in the decisions on my treatment plan going forward. I would recommend Cooley Smiles for anyone looking for a new dental group.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Omar Wahidi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcfB3CEPzBELpjMV9iG9IlmrUfI23ZzKOrFHHEpUp19Havg7T79A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I actually look forward to my appointments here! Dr. Aisha Hakeem recently fixed a problem area that had been bothering me for years, and now I don't even think about it anymore—it’s like the issue never existed. My filling looks great, feels natural, and passed the follow-up X-ray with flying colors. Colleen is a wonderful hygienist; she’s super friendly and my cleaning was top-notch. The office is clean, comfortable, and the whole team is incredibly hospitable. Highly recommend if you want quality dental care","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mercy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYJQrWtTJEkpSSwNpt7sBtGLL2ePXRqrbWn1QOYTrLUYTIvb7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐️ ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️\nI absolutely love Cooley Smiles dental team! Every visit with Dr. Kelly , Dr. Micaela, and my amazing hygienist Colleen is such a great experience. I also love visiting with Amy and Nonna — the whole team makes me feel so welcome. From the moment I walk in, they greet me like I’m coming home. They are truly exceptional at what they do — professional, gentle, and so caring. Each time I come in, my expectations are exceeded. You can feel how much pride they take in their work and how much they genuinely care about their patients. I always leave feeling confident and grateful to have found such a wonderful team. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cade Herbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBtTFzE0d2rmrjB0JEt0gaiVbeJc4wVY86o7V2gHFo17ZQMg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Damn grateful to found a dentist office that I look forward to visiting each and every time. An amazing and effective staff. If you were in the Kenmore, Bothell, Woodinville or Lake Forest Park area I could not suggest this facility more. Thanks for the great chat as always Cherelle!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damishetty Vamshi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbh-xPoYLiTmBlJFqxwdOlMj_04sCn2xxQ90u_yPYM4WWiZqdu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Cooley Smiles in Kenmore today! Karen, the hygienist, is hands down the best I’ve ever had — gentle, thorough, and incredibly professional. The whole team made me feel comfortable and cared for. Highly recommend Cooley Smiles to anyone looking for top-notch dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauren Squaglia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJdByvSH_XnwDhnn35NbDNmm7G0g43wuSGpyQAQaOFEcIugazcX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a great place! I am very particular about my teeth! I have never had a cavity and I am 45 years old and I take prevention seriously. This place is amazing. Hi-Tech, knowledgeable staff. Great equipment. It feels like going to a spa day! My teeth have never been cleaner and I have tried many dentists. I am set. This is the place to go if you want high quality care. My dental technician was just so thorough and my teeth feel amazing! I can't wait to come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debra Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIcTaqM65EEl6OIakS5cB84D2jyfVWsVsq1XcozlZ2iodLPqg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Cooley Smiles as a new patient and was super impressed from start to finish. The team was professional, thorough, and clearly attentive to every detail. The entire facility was spotless and welcoming, which really added to the experience. Overall, a great first visit — highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
