eusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF3GsmO9kCPHNZdoKEch8emcmiXznU3AC7BP3f3kAbMWYNoIeveA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our family has been long time clients of Accent Dental.  We have always been happy with the care we receive. Now my 86yo mom is a client also and she is treated with very tender careful hands while still meeting her dental needs. Thank you Accent Team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hafiz Huda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWH71JbNJHX-5AwYLyPQA4GY16yE6bBpt5YFtDTa9kQmThyGgHNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been coming here for years. Super friendly stay and it took me years to get back into the swing of things. Dr. Fernunson always has a cool and friendly approach... And no one gave me guilt or shame about the condition of my teeth. Things are all good now and I'm a big fan of this practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ingrid Perry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8CY28cyrX_1-8uunIAMCNyZ65DUDEHMO0KGLrKyGpXuEZ_5I4wg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I scheduled my dental appointment only after confirming that the office accepted my insurance, both through my provider and OpenCare. However, when I arrived, the receptionist informed me that because the visit involved a panoramic x-ray, I would need to pay out of pocket. This was unexpected and confusing, especially since my insurance covers x-rays as part of a routine cleaning.\n\nWhat’s most frustrating is that the office refused to proceed with the appointment, despite having verified insurance coverage beforehand. I wasn’t given a clear explanation as to why the panoramic x-ray was required or why it wasn’t covered, and no alternative was offered. The lack of communication and flexibility felt unprofessional and disappointing.\n\nI hope this feedback helps improve transparency and patient experience in the future","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Hyndman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrWCTDF0CwlsAvWBS9mHJCYmsg61E2IKgbjO06oQXFKyUTmTOyuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been having all my dental work done at this office since about 1973. I won't go anywhere else. They are welcoming, professional, and thorough in all they do. I always look forward to my teeth cleaning. 😄","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tara DeVeau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV541y2GVPvg1Ux7DfHI2wamE1FlmNQ4x29WUJ5yGuDVSvs9O-BIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was involved in an accident that left my front tooth chipped and Accent Dental fit me into their schedule quickly and repaired my tooth perfectly! So professional and kind. I couldn't have asked for a better new patient experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Coe Hutchison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7BbCMiD7eb5hVJWu_FqIqYlYhPvRAHBZRA8BZyy6go_UqoQ0LYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Welcoming, extremely clean. A gentle, comfortable cleaning. We have been going to this dental practice for 45 years. What more can we say.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWOwR79ZtV48UfKC58GeJXTOQjaARSGrp3T0ixfcU602b7OEbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Caballero, Krystee, and Brenda are the best. I haven't been to the dentist in over 5 years and needed a crown for my cracked tooth. Today's my first day and I felt welcomed, and well taken care of. Dr. Caballero is very skilled because he drilled my tooth to a stub and didn't feel any pain. Krystee made my crown and it looks amazing 😭 I look forward to all my future appointments!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Myra Beltran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3mVHYTJZ4cxDrgCG_y9zuYT-ONKsnRVw2G08YUnJy34tAKBjk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience during my recent dental visit. From the moment I arrived, the staff was warm, welcoming, and highly professional. The clinic was clean, well-organized, and followed proper hygiene protocols, which made me feel safe and at ease.\n\nMy hygienist and dentist  was thorough and gentle throughout the procedure. They took the time to explain everything clearly, answer my questions, and ensure I was comfortable. I especially appreciated the personalized care and attention to detail.\n\nThank you for making my visit feel smooth and reassuring. I’m grateful for your excellent service and will definitely recommend your clinic to family and friends.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
