s":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Matt Berg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV60CjdgJZA0vUN_rMamnjJS2_qGRXBPlLah_CLQtX2GaAmBDWIDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wooden Creek Dental is absolutely top-notch! They’ve always been prompt, professional, and incredibly accommodating. When I recently chipped a tooth, they were able to see me the very same day, and Dr. Goel repaired it flawlessly in record time. Every experience I’ve had with their team has been fantastic—they truly go above and beyond for their patients. Additionally, the one thing I love about them is that there is very little small talk. So, great dentist, practice for you introverts :)\n\nI highly recommend Wooden Creek Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvscXK4sCwxp4qYSO54dbO4ABMgCg-4c8eM2t8sqfwIXPtQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience coming to Woodin Creek Dental. Everyone was great from the front office, the assistants, the doctor's, and the hygenists. Can't recommend this office enough. They make sure you're comfortable and well taken care of.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adi Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpeJ3kXXaLk1mzMat9-l6sTbnx8COB_QIZZAZUOcx1QrhFQt6IWw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've been using Woodin Creek for a few years now and are all very happy with the level of service. Justin the hygienist is probably the best hygienist I've ever had.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Natalie Catone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSdQuk6IePLloI6uS_G3EbUL6Cqm-6VUzQDOulRSqPOL9gdKMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fast, courteous and efficient. I had a dental emergency and they fit me in late on a weekend for a quick assessment and had treatment within a few days.  Receptionists are very polite and welcoming,  technicians are professional and caring and the dentist was able to preform my procedure without pain and quickly. Glad I found a new dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Walt Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFNWHBOF1hMn_-lkGP5zvrrsAuqSjHGiYyDw9RLnn_IXPIbNk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I’ve been going here for more than 3 years. All my previous experiences were pleasant. But my recent visit was definitely below my expectations.\n\nThe dental hygienist was unprofessional and rude. She forgot to clean my lower teeth and came back to it after she said everything is done. The cleaning process was also very unpleasant. The chair was dirty with mud on it.\nI can tell how she hated this job and she really doesn’t care how the patient feels.\n\nI learned from the front desk that she is temporarily working here. I will go somewhere else if my next appointment is still like this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Agosti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKeNENMmZBzWizr2vom2crmZut_T1JfGLvnuKqIDWBs7NrMuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Started going to Woodin Creek Dental when the costs at my dentist started to go up dramatically as they moved into a nicer location and seriously upgraded their office decor.  So, that's where my money was going.  I tried Woodin Creek when they had a special offer and as I only needed a cleaning I thought I'd give it a shot.  That was over 5 years ago and the treatment has been first rate.  It's been mostly cleaning every 6 months, but have also replaced a crown there and the work they did on the crown was better than my expensive dentist.  Perfect fit the first time and haven't had any issues since.  They are always on time, do awesome work and at a very good price.  I think this is the first review I have ever written and they deserve it and should be recognized.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Rosales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU540d1vmEzwMmcxCaY-STTEpMoL84BSgb20snENzPkbwYpYxXfjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Wang is the best dentist I have ever had. If you are looking for an effecient and patient doctor who can communicate well, this is the place to go. My last visit was great and my teeth felt clean as promised. I highly recommend booking an appt with her for anything. Thank you woodin creek dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurie M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlpI_bmHj7M_hCb5MtgtqcK2v3iHJ7JzLMxDwWdvIYOIGA5QDj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been to this office  a few times now.  I am impressed with the care from beginning to end.  The front staff is helpful and friendly.  The assistants in the back are professional and make you feel comfortable.  The doctors are excellent and I always feel like I am in good hands.  They are quick to respond to urgent matters.  I didn’t even feel the injections!!  I would (and do) highly recommend Woodin Creek Dental to anyone who wants top notch care and service.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
