ntist that I once liked very much but she too turned out to have a very bad attitude when I brought up a subject but she didn't like regarding my teeth and a piece of equipment that they gave me. She even went so far as to suggested I get my records so that I can transfer to another dentist that's closest to me. Why would she suggest such a thing? Harvest came very far because I like their dentistry at first. And then with bad attitudes running rampant around there for the younger dentist and some of the staff, I will in fact go to another dentist. Outrageous, is the only word that I have for it. She brushed off my concerns when it wasn't something that she wanted to hear. By the way, the first receptionist that was there for a long time said that she no longer liked working there after the new dentist came in. New generation, new attitude? Change your ways Are you going to lose a lot of customers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anita Watley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBm04xrEjwILmVtMZ7opSTHj1slql1e5R82xKlSyVCM15-ww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr’s NGO and VO are professional and extremely personable. The clinic is clean and inviting. I was at ease and they did an amazing job with this nervous Nelly. I highly recommend them. They care about dental health.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stacy Reed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhOKwSyOxr_e4Kqf4eo4v6gxfK7tN3u7vX0QirzOyijd1-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Patient for over 15 years. Dr Vo is kind, efficient, knowledgeable and does excellent work. And now, her daughter has joined her and definitely a chip off the brilliant block!!\nYou will be grateful to find dentists that care and have the skill to accomplish amazing dental work. Check them out.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Silver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBd4l-yLxCTHhmzKw8bBqJlnqpJsqcplxjb9ZLpKIfBvBgfWe6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a patient for over 20 years and they’re like family. My first experience was when I had dental pain and Dr.Vo came in on a Sunday to help relieve the pain. It’s the best service and care. The employees are awesome! Would highly recommend to anyone looking for a dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Parwinder Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgXC6uoTSHxK4Tn7no_mLfcnv1Sd4BqLUAeO_xdYktYNmeVm_m=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"NSD is doing teeth removal and dentures for my mom, they were very thorough and planned it out pretty well, my mom is very happy with the teeth removal so far, will follow up on the dentures later when get them in couple of weeks. So far so good.I would recommend this clinic to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Javary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4TA4a-Ydegj257I1QWV-ezTXdofte2cyuXboToBoG4cDmVrk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going here recently to get my wisdom teeth removed along with cleaning and other things like braces. Dr. Vo is very professional and knowledgeable with her work making the process quick and easy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelan Porter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGIcnqxVVgZz1M0as8gqfYHj2_VGYLh8D1zG8Gw_NNhbyyB_A9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coming to Northshore Dental Center to get my bite fixed with braces has been a great experience over the past year. Before my procedure, I lost my ability to bite things like lettuce and always felt vague jaw pain. Now, having my teeth straight and aligned it is such a relief! I can eat normally! And, the biggest plus of all, I have my smile back!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
