ngs","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Pamela Leong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhtupLGvsGHuZRyhfZ6pm7rZsOUlq6_8mwhTtkCM53ZlmnVm4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finding a dentist who is both highly competent and has excellent chairside manner can be challenging, but Dr. Robinson exceeds expectations. I immediately felt confident in his expertise and appreciated his clear, thoughtful communication. He is very patient-focused and took the time to explain options and alternatives that had not been presented to me previously.\n\nThe examination was gentle and exceptionally thorough—one of the most comprehensive I have ever had. Dr. Robinson's assistant, Elsa, was also outstanding, and the receptionist was welcoming and helpful. Overall, it was an excellent experience, and I highly recommend this practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Don Phillips","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIEXdbluv-XNjXvmYc8NOEIgMukEwVllUl7iCKvmdrswGBSzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first experience with Robinson Dental was great!  As a new customer I was not sure what to expect.  On time, work began right  away and was promptly completed.  The work atmosphere is outgoing, friendly and not rushed.  My dental needs were provided promptly, carefully and in a very positive manner.  I would highly recommend them to anyone needing this type of service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig Sanderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDAYNXQ2P45jaok1itFKRBSWEfM8FXMoenTUazRLQxJeR_8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Robinson Dental if you’re looking for a family friendly office.  I’ve been with them for over 30 years and Dr. Robinson’s staff is excellent!  He seems to constantly stay up to date on cutting edge practices.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria Albanese","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2BhvsadZwSKe8jf4r4-1KOLnfVlaYXutwzb21Z8qODMOJlTo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Robinson Dental for over 40 years. I use to see Dr. Don, now It's his son, who I still call Don sometimes....\nThey have always been very fair \u0026 very good to me. I highly recommend if you are in the area \u0026 need a great dentist.\nCheers to Robinson Dental.\nVictoria","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJB0YObydLOn2_OqY19PavHrSL0rsrM2DS0e9jMKZ4bEJ4FIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place!   I’m 77 years old with no insurance.  I went to another dentist that wanted to pull all my molars and the cost was astronomical.  Dr Robinson fixed just what was needed for now.  His office is amazing and so comfortable.  He fixed my issues immediately.  I had already waited a month from another dentist that didn’t even  fix my issues.  Dr Robinson fixed my issues the same day.  His staff is great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diane Farkas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKU_0Yb7dTWDarMWSaBzMpDGhrYSi_EqKCfsaCRIosiqDWWcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Robinson Dental has been our dentist for 46 years, both Dr Robinson Senior, and now his son Dr Brent Robinson. Always great service, wonderful office staff, and Dr Brent is always able to work with any challenge, problems, and sound dental advice. The years with both father and son have been very effective for maintaining oral health,  helpful, and always a great office staff and atmosphere.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"shari smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVm7wmH8P0RaytFGereKARVTFGGptuVc5Q5EKZ3cKtvP58nSHTV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely the best all-around dental experience I’ve ever had.  My teeth have not looked so shiny and my gums so healthy. Everyone from Dr. Robinson, the hygienist, the assistant and the front desk manager were first class.  I’m excited about this new relationship!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patricia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvgTJu97HXAx0OeMpQXDLi_kkQMoiX_zd6wM6ie5FJnFoBJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going to this Dentist for over 32+years. Great Dentist and staff. Dr Robinson keeps up to date on all the latest dental procedures. He is a proficient and excellent professional.  He is ethical and caring. Would recommend this Dental office to all.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
