itive experience at Penny Creek Family \u0026 Implant Dentistry in Mill Creek. From the moment I walked in, I felt comfortable, heard, and genuinely cared for. I left feeling well-informed, confident in this team,  and incredibly grateful.\n\nThe dentist is not only highly knowledgeable, but it’s very clear he truly cares—about your teeth and about you as a person. That level of care carries through the entire office. From the dental assistant to the receptionist/finance manager, every single person was personable, thoughtful, genuine, understanding, and compassionate.\n\nThis is the first dentist I’ve seen for this journey, and I honestly feel extremely grateful and lucky to have found them. It felt like I was exactly where I was supposed to be—my angels picked a good one. I highly recommend Penny Creek Family Dental to anyone looking for a team that combines professionalism with real human care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Falcon 94","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXW9g4pkHklJGRXb1jQfjg6pDdrmrvki9s8oV259fv2LOYCdz0i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So thankful for the entire team at Penny Creek Dentistry! Had to get a molar filled and it was done so well! They made sure I was comfortable the entire time…so grateful! My whole family goes here…thank you so much!! So grateful to have Dr. Lundgaard and Dr. Slocum as our dentists and the entire group!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"GRWTH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT2OYz4JtSyf4tqep_pDcmaSGQ4sDJ4J3oLR-mQe6YuUVE150=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"ZERO STARS!!!\nMARCI at the front desk is extremely rude and displays clear microaggressions. I have been coming to this office since I was in middle school, but I will never return because of my experience with her.\nI called to make an appointment regarding a filling they did, which was a terrible job and has left me in pain a year later. Instead of helping, I was met with attitude and no concern.\nI wish I had known better back then. I strongly recommend avoiding this place if you can. You may end up in pain years later, and when you reach out for help, they will not support you or take responsibility. Be careful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Stephens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjlHgaMDENp4Hv06hEiTGU82UFBmc6REwle6X_cJ5j_8Bbpx1i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Im at the beginning of completely restoring my mouth and I found this dental implant ad for penny creek online by researching myself and boy did I get blessed by the grace of G*d this is one absolutely amazing and comforting place, I actually look forward to going to the dentist for the first time in my life saying that is crazy however they are all wonderful nice and very welcoming right off the bat, it feels like a family oriented place. The dentist was very gental and very thorough when explaining my options with clarity thank you to all the staff at my favorite dentistry office see you soon 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Boyd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAi30ZgjH9wKZaplQYHtHjGlkNSWyVnnL8NeEBxy6L_sjAoZ6z=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The easiest oral surgery ever.  Preparing me for the procedure was organized and included thoughtful things to make me comfortable. The doctor is highly skilled while also gentle enough to avoid any unnecessary trauma.  Although surprisingly I had little to no pain post surgery I was sent home with a complete care kit, just in case. The whole experience was incredibly well done and I felt very much that my comfort was as of much importance as the surgery itself.  Thankyou Dr Slocum, Jen and the whole wonderful team.\n-Karen B","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jackson Montemayor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYSU_O4c1cUmKYMG6k_EP_f0UQw1obARbwmUPQi4nJCRaZOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this dentist on 9/18/2025 at 3pm. Took me in right away, didin’t even have to wait. Doctor was nice and experienced. Teeth cleaning went well, as well as examination. I was able to schedule my next appointment right away at the most convinent time for me. This dentist has always been great, I would highly recommend coming here. Thanks for such great service, Penny Creek Dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaviya venkatesan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSHsstm6N5BUckg91jFQMQDsit0SJc4TEFq_rVjm0wywQPBFQr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had my wisdom tooth extracted at Penny Creek Family and Implant Dentistry and the experience was great. The dentist was skilled and caring, and the whole process was smooth. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joan Weisberg Beyerlein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDL0FVk9Xl8TtB4GIOEc0YCfQfpsGZNbxZC_ht4Fed_-33Sg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had dental implant surgery. Dr Slocum is amazingly skillful. He explained the procedure during the surgery. The surgery went more quickly than I anticipated and I was totally pain free during the surgery. He checked with me regularly to make sure I was not experiencing any discomfort.\nHis nurse was also quite skillful and attentive, as well as friendly\nThe entire staff at Penny Creek is friendly and really helpful\nHighly recommended","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
