roughout. Today my smile 😁 is perfect. Thank you so much. I'm a forever client and fan. 😁😁","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lavena Staten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJ11wPF_kwNc82wfN6j7tz5A6MCI84Q2JdUCdW-TgwJVX1nsX-Pg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"BEWARE!!! i went to this dentist office for three years. and every time i came in, i was told i have several cavities and i got them filled.\n\nlast time i went in, i was told i had six cavities that needed filled. i was suspicious and i decided to switch to another dentist because i take excellent care of my teeth and only had infrequent cavities before coming to A Dental \u0026 Denture.\n\nthe new dentist said i have ZERO cavities, nothing that even kinda resembled a cavity. sooooo take that into consideration if you go to this dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theresa Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8itRpdOlr43RnbqirQ_KnupLbMWHvOt8U2o09t5AxG2vG9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Dental is wall to wall friendly, professional staff. They are great at providing dental care and always explained a procedure clearly and accurately. Anyone looking for a new dental clinic or looking to change their dentist, I would like to recommend this team of friendly and knowledgeable people for your dental care;  from cleaning to dentures you won’t be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Alspaugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOpMbwnnJYZAczJo3jWUCm92rq8Ned85bMsakaasLz_J7gE_9B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing job. Only took a few hours. Very nice staff. Can't even tell it was snapped apart widthwise across the middle. Reinforced with inserts. Probably stronger than it was originally.  I'm so happy 😊.  Wish I had taken a better picture of their very nice office. Update December 14,24 the dentures I had fixed are still perfect 👌","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37aqfi_ZVs4xfGXUyLPE-LfDpB6_aWJ3Z8-WdpcKTU91rQKOnvNzsI6ZbLsXHNO6PB8Xq3WbDKo9PqkNHoDSQs6B1PLyeDvZPd7rW_Kb1q7IDeySJ91_VT-w90xaitqTCynxRH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0uh9JJg_PXAtE0COXQET8KXKdxRZHcvx_82NqzknEEmJ2HRLLj1DyPKRztKMJryxMHLkv5GZzWb6_zsu_zKMeoKvTUEZlQS5Wq_d2OPRGxON4pWyvPmtbDAs6_Tv8v4TcsqiphSQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Julia Irick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9qOAmSFoXOr_axX8ZEbmxA73rHfMe4ScBKu9kEpUK4CRIM-cHRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Angela, Dr. Hatem, Sarah at the front desk, all the lovely dental assistants, you are incredible! Seriously could not have had a better experience getting extractions and dentures (scary!). They make me feel comfortable, safe, and like a friend every time I am there. They eased my anxieties and worked with my finances. Truly the best place to get dental work done.  Thank you for all you do!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danny Bou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLX2ImaI5bBk0RI9po6K3560EmdMIB9qzWuoPFILK6zcgI9vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family has been going to this office for years. The cleaning and fillings done is  painless. They are very attentive and thorough- also in explaining the best oral hygiene for my needs. They go above and beyond to ensure I was informed about my treatment. They are like family. Thank you A Dental \u0026 Denture!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julius Debro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3WLHksQYhQ77hXod2GQlAs2FOlAScuOS8-LJ0tWCXGyTnfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a wonderful place to get dental work completed at A Dental and Denture in NORTH SEATTLE.. last week I had to get my annual cleaning. as usual, was greeted by Angela and the staff. started on time, finished on time. my wife was going to pick me up but was late.  Dr MELIZZA had seen a small cavity.instead of making another appointment. he decided to put me back in there and fix it while I was still there. Took ten minutes and no charge. great place, wonderful staff, always helpful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kylie Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWElCnAIC2xPFvv4NlXHoj8RnFA75FSoXkBOvhL9k6ROUI53Iv4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw Dr. Amar for TMJ and a cleaning. Every step from the front desk associate, to the dental associate and Dr. Amar was fantastic. The dentist can be an intimidating experience, but they all were personable and knowledgeable. They didn’t push more than what you needed and I truly appreciate that. So grateful to have found them.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
