-/ALV-UjXQxdpyhXjAR2cJwfDnhN2RxFofDfX-XxtI9ktbi05deOu0Qqh6aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kenmore Smiles was my third and final try at a dental practice home when I moved to Kenmore. Dr Mott and the entire team make excellent look easy, always going above and beyond to provide the best care. You should check them out!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rosemary Winquist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqhtBbrk2N4Mznq2ZLHLbXpmhvoWczr1rWVZIU8yKG_4p4ogqQdw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this practice. They are professional, efficient, reasonable, and thorough. They don't try to fix things that don't need fixing, and they genuinely care about their patients' overall health. The front desk is well-equipped to handle insurance companies, and I never feel pressured to pay immediately until they get a clear answer about what is covered and what is not. They are truly the best I've had since my beloved dentist, Doug Smart DDS, ended his practice of 60 years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Lien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3_-bo3C7X2EMpi7wcawK8wrBawnUc1oj9KfEcmXV2mUoXlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love my hygienist Dan so friendly and kind. Dr Mott always makes me feel welcome. They really listen and know and remember things about you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zach Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIIZ4y_NOQd93wLvNs--Wv9xFrCStuYxs4u_4imvesTbQ9Zs0bvA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a very pleasant experience. The staff were friendly, thoughtful, and gave me both detailed advice and the reasonings behind them.\n\nFrom the new patient form to the dental cleaning itself, I could feel that they've dedicated a considerable amount of effort to make this as comfortable of an experience as possible. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chun Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVNDehkG0Acr-UP_kg0n_qumaB5xFdtscy10LAh_6PnZf1Qw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience at Kenmore Smile has been wonderful. The office is clean, modern, and everyone is warm and friendly.\nDr. Morgan is warm, thoughtful, and helpful. Her treatment plans are always practical and in my best interest. My dental hygienist, Dan, is  kind, patient,  careful and always does an excellent job.\nOverall, every visit is a pleasant experience！","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Jasinski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxgKYrmrJs11jVJcKy0ZXX5i7g0sHCupgFuNyNb4XaB9caNgr5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kenmore smiles was suggested by some community members after our dentist retired early due to health issues. I have been very happy with care here so far after a couple of appointments. They are very kind and organized","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"X. Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-KL8QvJmfyi4VPs8Cvpn81wYYVYU4D2SpOTbOSYCMogOohQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at Kenmore Smiles Family Dentistry! Dr. Bradley Mott and his team are incredibly professional, kind, and attentive. From the moment I walked into their modern, welcoming office, I felt relaxed. The staff is friendly and made scheduling a breeze with their convenient text and call reminders. Dr. Mott took the time to explain everything thoroughly, ensuring I was comfortable and informed about my treatment. Highly recommend Kenmore Smiles for anyone looking for a caring and skilled dental practice.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
