:true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"jose roque","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFWIZyV069ojTrHUYRKJd_dEr8hWEhpWwR0r7RswBTZXRetps=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really want to thank Dr. Lin for the great job he does. My last procedure was an extraction, and everything went great—it was super fast and smooth.\nThe whole team is awesome. Elizabeth, Dr. Lin’s assistant, was super helpful, and Lidia ñ at the front desk made me feel welcome right away. For my cleanings, Kat always does an amazing job.\nI definitely recommend them if you’re looking for great care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dagim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbhEkMVWXcUvIQKCljA6rkziOXL7B7L0gvmWT1SuR-aB9lDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lin is truly incredible. I had all of my restorative work done here, including fillings and a crown, and the experience exceeded my expectations at every step. The quality of care was outstanding, and everything was explained clearly so I always felt comfortable and informed. I was really nervous but they put me at ease.\n\nWhat really sets this place apart was how personal the experience felt. Dr. Lin and the team genuinely took the time to get to know me, and I was even checked on the day after each visit with a follow up phone call to make sure I was doing ok. Something you don’t see often and really speaks to how much they care.\n\nThe atmosphere is warm, friendly, and welcoming, and the entire team is made up of great people who make you feel at ease from the moment you walk in. I highly recommend Complete Dentistry to anyone looking for a skilled, compassionate dentist and a team that truly guides you through your care.\n\nYou’re in excellent hands here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tuva Chaudhry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK8mjATq1d3-S78dxDV-YOpU513mSiJN-M_h5pj_9vhqlujZA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came into the office yesterday to have my aligner attachments placed by Dr. Lin and his assistant Elizabeth, and they were both so attentive and got me set up quickly. The front desk staff was also warm which made the whole experience even better. :)\n\nIt’s now the next night and my aligners feel snug but still comfortable…I was able to sleep through the night just fine and feel like I’m adjusting. I’ll be changing my trays every two weeks with a total of 10 trays in my treatment plan, so a total of 5 months.\n\nDr. Lin let me know that if I have any discomfort he’s happy to take a look and make adjustments. So far so good and I’m really looking forward to finally getting the smile I’ve wanted for years!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3K_SOhQqEyF8Yq0akdu6r_gW_TgSs3fykbc9mcTy9eAGXziIdiRI50ZlAz3IPrdv34FPX-kjxX4GNQrU1L-rZ9mht2tmsnxySuJuVMGSgIL8JXEJyY13o1XADIlB4tsI653StFsPYaq91X=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-4"},{"Name":"Angel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJY-NB1EQmFfPM4qIEijDxv7wxs1SuHAl1fU6UuMI0HGrQ8h4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at Complete Dentistry. Doctor Lin was professional, compassionate, and gentle during my visit for a filling. He answered all of my questions clearly, which made me feel stress-free and comfortable. Overall my experience with the dental team was great, I felt heard. I would definitely refer my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raquel Madrigal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfWEk2hbc8Faqpwzd3Awe3SiB959e4F4PYr_6ZJh2OCsTVjyYB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first visit at Complete Dentistry and was blown away by how kind and patient staff were. Since the moment I walked in I was greeted with a friendly smile. Jan, who did my cleaning, was amazing. She was super friendly and provided dental hygiene education in such a kind manner. The dentist was also very through in explaining my next steps. Definitely recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Brehmer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuSecsp20YzBtzwaLbInyB-8ypEgKRLp3aHY4Dy4Q3Bxf4ZpA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to complete dentistry for a number of years now. As a senior with mobility issues, the staff are very kind and helpful when I need assistance. My dentist and hygienist are very professional, thorough, gentle and always answering my questions. I have felt well cared for and recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Basma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIjIyK-sznLqWN09JUwyMAzdgObf0e4xjiHCe_-YLx5KJBPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Complete Dentistry with Dr. Lin! From the moment I walked in, the staff was warm, professional, and made me feel comfortable right away. Dr. Lin is incredibly skilled, patient, and thorough—he takes the time to explain everything and makes sure you’re at ease throughout the visit. The office is modern, spotless, and very welcoming, which adds to the overall positive experience. I felt well cared for, and the results exceeded my expectations. I highly recommend Dr. Lin and Complete Dentistry to anyone looking for a dentist who truly cares about their patients!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4YOhJo4QMJvcy_av8yzuSlJJqZHOsql9_OsrdAFqzpJuNbZfipQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was visiting from California and came in for a last minute visit with Dr. Lin. Brandy was very helpful in answering all of my questions making sure that my insurance was accepted (Blue Shield CA). The whole process was painless as Dr. Lin was gentle while fixing my cavity. Also, I appreciated that the assistant Joseph was really attentive in making sure I didn’t choke on any of the saliva/water throughout the operation 😂. Great staff, felt really comfortable and at ease.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
