"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Julia Olson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1a0YXe7gDnGXBWlrPd2numQj1HP-5oqjDfQUVxMYX5GbWGHM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wouldn't trust anyone else with my dental care. Dr. Priya and her staff are so welcoming and knowledgeable. I have a very complex dental history and Dr. Priya and her staff are always making sure to take extra care with my cleanings and other dental needs. You can trust Dr. Priya and her team to make the best decisions for your health and work with you to help ease financial strain. The amazing location and clean office is the cherry on top of the phenomenal care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3MnpsD_ADO_XRvAwn2WNE9ebU_vmrarRKIuZKNH6S6-s1n4ZWSnjTdfe6wehi3Sa8g8PD9T7fbKDZfcdHehzsh3btzsyz1Ps3kW-yMo4OO7Olok_nUL58dmm1BnbrBr21tIb-87rpM3xvf=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2GzhPhE7SsIfZMZ1ULVQ26tbx_W8WKk27_biC4dSXhxVm358IQyexaL8GWZRs8qdcPi-uK3jI8mRZHlv14NX9o8oMKfS2hnFlXmIc7l2WTVp_ZhqLEXpT3SG8-G3aMb0QfYUsBNF0W4Xj7=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn02jRwUVqMWhbWVoavocm6uYMqJOPeJBjodm4v2k9YeYcNsZHiO4gW-xXFpSD51lYHSs483qRHd5veqqWldVlUTVpM-1HSY4CpPO5lBVncR5b369NKuaclX2pUXW9aN-dSVgbZNq9QSeqks=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-9"},{"Name":"Sharon Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKM763bZWUfkGQUvHLvS2zFyEMAnFbBDU2rs2c8Y1L0CUOX8w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very professional, detail in her artistry design of my dentures \u0026 their color. I now have a beautiful smile \u0026 a snug perfect fit. I highly recommend PS Dental Studio. Thank you so very much. Your whole staff was so kind to me. I don’t like going to the dentist. If I had had a dentist like Dr. Preya in my past I would have gone to the dentist willingly \u0026 wouldn’t have had to have dentures. But I am very pleased with my beautiful smile.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Webster","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJD-Ow6eGhTLg0tIIuj5aa_aeyR_O3RAmey7_b4Mfp1FU7cXA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I truly loved my experience with Dr. Priya and her team. I am a new patient who has some dental anxiety because of previous dentists. I saw the same dentist for 15 years, then he sold his practice to a company. After that I saw a different doctor every visit. It felt like no one read my file or cared enough to give quality care because they knew they would probably never treat me again.\n\nThat is not the case with Dr. Priya. Since she is the only doctor in the office, you can tell she truly cares about her patients and wants each person to have the best experience. I needed a few fillings and her injections were almost painless, something I had never experienced before. She has such positive energy, which helped calm my nerves, and she clearly has excellent knowledge.\n\nI am so relieved to have found my dentist. I highly recommend her to anyone in the area. Even if you are not close, she is worth the drive.\n\nA huge shoutout to my hygienist Kyle as well. You were a blessing. Thank you to the entire team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jeff Downing","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYSZktIfJrC58fWgwExQV1KlUkN40gWlZ8lUSPCnQc9wQd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Priya is a miracle worker in my opinion. I’ve been seeing dentists for over 70 years and she is by far the most committed to her craft and patients then any other professional I’ve worked with. The office and staff are light hearted and fun which really helps with a nervous patient like myself but at the same time very serious about the patients oral health. She’s changed my life and given me the pleasure of smiling again. Thank you Dr. Priya","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1RpI9mnWhdxa3kBpunQg9kHDl9ne48n00gVZCZStJj_VBQjMzw6g_0fFCw0TGLFzEN04immIVbekHXjh-IsjdMIDW-BfE8_xFOMxNbx-WsCNQ8jdkiNomYXgsi5Fo9Y2WGb_b50Zyfhhmt=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-3"},{"Name":"Shiyi Pickrell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3-WJX7TFI-NCZ5uY3e2FaVkHsJ6Up6lK4-jZVtPxAXwwhDxpq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Changing from previous 1 star to 4 star.\nMy family had been with Dr. Priya for many years. In general we are happy with her and her staff. The dental hygienists and Dr. Priya are always very friendly and thorough. In Aug 2025, the dentist said two old crowns or tooth surface were cracking which I trusted their assessment. I paid my estimated copay prior to the operation and had 2 crowns done. To my surprise, after the operation the insurance company denied the claim which would mean that I would have to pay another thousand dollar out of my pocket. Over the next 5 months, I kept calling both the insurance and the office many many times, I was super frustrated because the insurance said they were waiting for additional supporting document from the office. The billing people from the dental office always told me to call the insurance company. Disappointed and frustrated, I shared the bad experience on google review. Then Dr. Priya personally took ownership of the situation and worked with the insurance company and straightened out the claim. Finally insurance approved the claim after 5 months and paid their shares. First of all, i appreciate Dr. Priya's dedication to her patients. Our family still come to her clinic and highly recommends it to other people. The biggest lesson learned here is for expensive procedures it is better to get insurance's pre-approval in advance to avoid any drama and surprise.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S. Henry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnDMRP_6kBSqwR-1cRU27zKdfs4ZbDgaHowHdAvnyIsMbDug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Priya is a wonderful and highly skilled dentist with a gentle, caring staff.\nHer dental studio can do it all in less time than I've ever spent at previous offices.\nDr. Priya's calm approach, thorough explanation of procedures and gentle care will put you at ease.  You could not be in better hands.  Highest recommendation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Garland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQdrrQE3snk5n5RWMsl9LU8cSbjnEe-BkJXlp-GRu4sdxQKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Priya has been my dentist for years and is the only dentist I will trust to perform my required dental work and maintenance. She is exceptionally skilled in all procedures that are offered, and will take the time to absolutely ensure you are satisfied with the results.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Athina Pugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaA2BC8eH5FVBap3VOOVGKEXMOR6jFub96_qq1hPpiGAqyEDE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a couple fillings and crown today. Louisa was my assistant and she was so gentle and there to assure me. Feeling better knowing my mouth is in a healthy state and at the same time I'm in Good hands. Thank you","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25SBem4HVE-3vAGXzE04oqhKMYUizo69IuJ99tmpkpoh9m4e_UyV_FtozjKECRMc0NdEpZnrm1HkW5jCSAmxyypDmn_XckQ2yo33V-UR9KYXQBjaYa1_PMm_U3fmOZc8QfDlfPSQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-26"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
