026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"/url?q=https://juanitabaydentist.com/general-dentistry/\u0026opi=79508299\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwjS1975psSUAxVGETQIHVg-MvAQqRkIHSgQ\u0026usg=AOvVaw1v43EWLbfd5N054Gkal4nm","source":"juanitabaydentist.com"},"owner":{"id":"115635737830172144190","name":"Juanita Bay Dentist (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115635737830172144190"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Totem Lake","street":"11321A NE 120th St","city":"Kirkland","postal_code":"98034","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Maria Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzpWrpcZ3wDqBsB5Huf4NniGNh89KgdPs5HiJcw-OVin2kAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Juanita Bay Dentist! The team is warm, friendly and professional. The office is welcoming and everyone made me feel comfortable throughout my visit.\nThe doctors took the time to explain everything clearly and made sure that I felt at ease during my treatment. You can tell that this place truly cares about their patients. I’m so grateful to have found dentists that I can trust! I highly recommend this office to anyone looking for exceptional care and service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clarice Cohn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiHUm2mZzUMqEOSsq2VeVN1MW09bQ2rOg0ScS13SWrFFayWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient for almost three years now, and have only had great experiences in that time! From basic cleanings with Max, to fillings and my first ever crown, I've been impressed with how the office stays current with new technology. Isn't it lovely to not dread going to the dentist?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wojtek Powiertowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzYD4iXHPLG7vq0kVv2000DOiFJ6DKFxgyFevdryy-T9vEQR4T=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Juanita Bay Dentist delivers consistently excellent care. The front-desk staff is organized, friendly, and efficient, making scheduling and check-in easy. The dental hygienists are thorough, gentle, and attentive, clearly explaining each step and ensuring comfort throughout the visit. Dr. Moua is outstanding—skilled, patient, and careful in both diagnosis and treatment. He takes time to answer questions, offers clear recommendations, and creates genuine confidence in the care plan. A well-run clinic with a team that makes every appointment smooth and reassuring.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kukkai M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYc5A3v5joFi8h7z9ivtCGK4bXrNGOsm0ePVRcI14s9Q1YIUWc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been seeing Dr Moua now for about 14 years and he is the best.   I’ve always been weary of dentists until now. I actually enjoy going in for cleanings now. I believe the most important part of a patient doctor relationship is trust and I found that with Dr Moua and his team. He is honest, direct, and kind which I appreciate. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Wen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo1FE8Pn1efPY90XriBFwA-zhxXQXzMEqNg-6htEIOPgZlMHb9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This office is always very clean and the front desk staff and hygienists are always friendly and easy going. The doctors are very interested in their work as they always seem to be looking to find new and modern techniques to improve the experience and care from my conversations with them. Today I got to try out their new fancy cleaning/polishing tool called the \"Woodpecker\". Definitely not the most appealing sounding name by the company that made it, but it was actually very smooth, comfortable and clean. The best thing was I got to go eat lunch immediately after the appointment without having to go to the restroom to swish forever trying to get the traditional grainy polish out between my teeth. That convenience was much appreciated today.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ash Effenberger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBMsz6VkZIX1GVG8AHxT4dcPowU3HKNiFatqQKfpeLDdvy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone here is absolutely amazing, I just finished my cleaning with Max who was amazing, very knowledgeable and patient with me. And Dr Moua checked in to see how my teeth are doing, I’m seeing such great improvement in all I’m doing and I’ve been with these guys for over 8 years now and dragged the rest of my family here lol these guys are great! Shout out to Hailey and Tammy you guys are the BEST!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Helmut Katzgraber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEQ3okIkPpOSHJV_9NVfg2o1Ve6I7xy3NdQHvjNw-Q5juHECKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far the best dentist I have had in my life. Not only are they passionate about their patients, they embrace the lastest tech and really ensure that no long-term problems emerge. Dr. Moua is a perfectionist -- something I really appreciate when seeing a dentist.\n\nAs a matter of fact, I moved to Denmark last year and come back to the Seattle Area for dental appointments. Speaks for itself.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeremy Pemble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNC8QC8vxYjmmUBK_DojGkktwtopm3covgNx8oKoHVAI7hp3e8xQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Mooua is an excellent dentist as is Max, their hygienist.  The optional, advanced water based cleaning system they have is also so much better than traditional cleaning methods. My family has been coming for years and highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
