 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=xNj6WQX4Y5V6XqrpTkLBew\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=242.20009\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://juanitafamilydentistry.com/contact/?y_source=1_NTU4MzQ4NTYtNzE1LWxvY2F0aW9uLnJlc2VydmF0aW9uX3VybA%3D%3D","source":"juanitafamilydentistry.com"},{"link":"https://www.zocdoc.com/practice/juanita-family-dentistry-59-60065?LocIdent=120731\u0026utm_source=reservewithgoogle\u0026utm_medium=seosynd\u0026utm_campaign=hai\u0026entity_id=pt_TqhSykk480-u1j0dgGiiwh-lo_c0_RSBdmO0CFcuA1dhdYFx-entity\u0026rwg_token=AFd1xnGkXCuP8s0M0ixONEh5T8-AkDryLz-v4i_em-XjOutOsb52Svczi6IwdbTz1-2Zix93-AnolEDi5J0VaM-oYc1iIND4bw%3D%3D","source":"zocdoc.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"104712091077575982700","name":"Juanita Family Dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104712091077575982700"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Inglewood-Finn Hill","street":"13611 100th Ave NE","city":"Kirkland","postal_code":"98034","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"CRB","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlWaz-CpLkCsoZ0m20cug9HZVANhz5-bVzKj-MEUnf_4jgXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had my new patient appointment and oh my goodness, this practice is amazing!!! I have dental anxiety and the team was so kind and understanding! Dj, Victoria and Dr. Pannu were so fast and efficient while answering all my questions, easing anxiety and coming up with an exceptional dental plan that I'm looking forward to! Jasmine, along with the front desk were also so warm and welcoming. I'll definitely be recommending juanita family dentistry to everyone i know!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lori Horst","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL29bwMcc9qUuJG_0FXgawjRZ42vUqG4sF735ZeJ8iI7KQRgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Chelsea Mortell  Petisme .. she is whip smart and reasonable with her fees.   I have been through 2 different hygienists here, both I loved and both moved and today I saw Sophie.  She was so thorough and gentle and I had a very positive experience.  She coaxed me into trying  the ultrasonic scaler, which I had bad experiences with in the past. It was great..she used a low setting and I handled it fine.  I love this office.  Chelsea doesn’t over recommend treatments and is supportive if you can’t afford to schedule immediately.  I have been with this office for over 10 yrs and I’m very happy with the care and patience they have given  me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Manhardt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURdYom5HaJiMFk3LwGMfgyMAPj0VrdmRIoJAYozNl67LsEHpe3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a disappointing experience at Juanita Family Dentistry earlier this week. I arrived for my 6-month exam/cleaning expecting to see my regular dentist, Dr. Tiffany Go, only to be informed halfway through my cleaning that she had left the practice and I would be seeing someone else today.\n\nWhile both the hygienist and the new dentist were kind and professional, the lack of communication about such a major change was really frustrating. Patients build relationships with their providers and being notified in advance of a provider’s departure is basic courtesy. Finding out mid-appointment very much felt like a bait and switch (especially after learning Dr. Go left months ago).\n\nI hope this practice improves its communication so other patients are informed of provider changes prior to their appointments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zixiao Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmh6WLtundqgALSnvrOnvyL110MFoGLfKfBhemWADGgDeWd3cj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Dr Chelsea was professional and seemed nice. The front desk and billing office did not meet expectations. I've called twice during business hours and both times it went to voicemail. My request for my own medical information has been slow. The specialist office also mentioned that they called twice to try and get the xrays.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandra Papesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-bo8HEKKHLVC1qKbGwFg__wO_n4u8KtDcC-XgOsD3psY3dBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This team is fantastic! Dr. Chelsea was amazing, the communication and explanation from everyone (from financial aspects to the actual dental work) was above and beyond, and I could tell the all of the staff cared. I do not have great reactions to dental work and they were very understanding and helpful to make sure my work got done with the least amount of stress and pain possible. Truly grateful for them all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Stanks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMZdOSTToaJnEjN4S_BRahr8-tM-ey5AXDC7D4slRwYWfw6Yku=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Chelsea is amazing! I had an incident this past May where I cracked one of my front teeth. Unfortunately the filling fell out this morning, and the team was able to get me scheduled and my tooth fixed within a few hours! It looks perfect!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Higa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSV1IlgV409391c0Ljf-LqrwUj-k02bExrE9w2DeUWuIKaP8HT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I received a call from Juanita because I hadn’t been to the dentist in years (I know, I know). I was a little embarrassed, but they mentioned they had an opening, and since I was going to be in town that weekend, I rearranged my schedule to get a cleaning. I usually see Dr. Tiffany and specifically asked if she would be my dentist. They even offered me a different time to make sure she was available.\n\nWhen I arrived, the front desk staff did not seem welcoming, which already set the tone. The hygienist who helped me was very kind and thorough, and I was happy with my cleaning overall. However, when it came time to see the dentist, I was surprised when Dr. Chelsea walked in. I had asked for Dr. Tiffany, but apparently her last day was the previous Thursday. This was not communicated to me at the time of scheduling, which made things feel very awkward and disappointing—especially since I went out of my way to confirm she would be there.\n\nMy mom, who was with me, also noticed that the front desk staff was rude. While I appreciated the hygienist’s care, the lack of communication and the front desk experience left a bad impression. Because of this, I most likely will not be returning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Natalia Pratsiuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmLC4UdGhbFctAkg4NrT-lIYGkHiMK3kNSU7A7JJqebwBhMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I sincerely recommend this clinic. True professionals work here, and the team is wonderful. They are always helpful, can see you the same day, or guide you on what to do next. I truly appreciate their care and attitude. Special thanks to the doctor!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
