5V6TGcnDU3sljPkMXNTvHeQ=w529-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=VFwkvcgPimRpBQyKAH_0_A\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=239.9665\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"112564198670001113492","name":"West Coast College of Dental Assisting (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112564198670001113492"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"18321 98th Ave NE #2","city":"Bothell","postal_code":"98011","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kaitlyn Guenther","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeEtmXfkqare_OLQxKZ11nfp9flba3oCtDk_RCHGsnXXxvIQIbDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alexis \u0026 Becky do an amazing job running their program. The school is perfect for someone who wants a lot of 1v1 time. The class is 10 people. Lots of lab time. You can work on other people in the class for an opportunity other than the mannequin, and makes for good laughs. And becoming more comfortable. Alexis gave me advice on how to get the job with little to no experience (outside of school) I got the offered a job after a working interview. Towards the end of the program you can get a job while still being in school which is so nice. If I had any questions she was very sweet and went over as many times as I needed to really get the hang of it. I enjoyed my time here, and would recommend it to others.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn07CpEItcFw-rp_EuNP387B5E2fjPKHxeUqdnapHFIRh9YsJE_dJRCWBHc3uFEKHbcr6dz16j0teU3YhmQeWo1HHw0nkDjtAISbUSPbkP4KfFeaFLAxRIQ2oEbh6LLviymW1BHYog=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3EJADxzswx2e5ujP3AgDZmnkvJlBapbs9v3DoPbbohndcybOlIArvsDX0mtVE-o2I8V3FcDjwL1WnORrb26SlEHiz6GXc_ui4J2YL7IQ5OED6Nsp_8FVMnET35lpyZyRhZfr0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2b0uwxouvpmHeIlUqZ_tG3pP9HWTUej-xXBXQKf7Y3iiPg57sOzH3hVAhUXhVS9rUXLBCBAD0-fXMUk701Hj7NpsuUNCr-soW1-B-3IG-M80ss3B_qy6fw-rgofHnez46Wdiit=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-11"},{"Name":"Ірка Прозапас","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlB-1fT3Loap_exmQ95Tk7CDqt9lqNvSFS1FzScQpk5cVvkbr0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"To be honest, this school was a joy for me, I was happy to come here, although sometimes it was difficult to understand some information, the teacher always helped in everything, always positive and kind to us, Alexis is a very nice and kind and very intelligent teacher. I recommend this school to everyone who would like to work as a dental assistant, it is the best school.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn09PQVTsVC2sSaLuQxtESaPfJUAkd3IBd8Dfv2cuCtq0UcOhuS1Fpk-KkLCJ6ygMO5ni5HEfnKC8N_USauDipZE8mEFEuM4j7I35fijffYI19mzo8xclqF4kXznhyiuLT83-iKD=k-no"],"When":"2024-3-6"},{"Name":"Marie Mosqueda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJ7b9qZjQXqtzrZgXy8nk6uV84wMUukPRlP5T8cxEazX7Hrw_mig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a good experience learning and training with such nice and amazingq instructors, Becky and Alexis. You will definitely learn a lot about dental assisting from them. They are immensely knowledgeable in their field. They are patient and very understanding, they extend efforts to help you and make sure you’d get the best training and preparation to be a great DA. The facility is clean and well organized. I would definitely recommend them in a heartbeat.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ttzNJMxOdQkF9v0FIqdVmvll1wnilO6F04xs5WqKmrKe-lyODHr6eQaNxBrEczaMDdKzKrX-YlDcPw7DRlMvaoD8NKZJeOnEkBvngiZ7EPDIgug8XRKo5Tbrqtr-I6L8IuOWK=k-no"],"When":"2021-11-8"},{"Name":"Karla Moon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpNSGhNiVZyoaqx8S8SSXftyQZpWzWImcLaO7bKXSDLIPDgAOBhA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such an amazing experience at this school! Alexis is great teacher. She is so patient and understanding. Always willing to give you extra time and help with things you are struggling with. She is very connected with her students and does so much to help us succeed. I would definitely recommend this school to anyone wanting to become a dental assistant!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kassidy Caporusso","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmJuOqI6pu_-XCCbvVeuuoj7lDX9n8SkBi-azgaKuz6rtdsv6F=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This school is so amazing! Alexis is the best teacher I’ve ever had. She makes sure that each and every student gets the best education possible. Thanks to her and the schools dummies that we practice on, I actually can have a career as a Dental Assistant. I am so thankful for this school and Alexis for her wonderful teaching abilities.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Iris Yin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0rZsN6WakYEBKN1hFsT7IyYKya1AlJ4LsyUurztOutT12Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Becky is one of the best instructors I've ever met in my life. She is so amazing, patient, and knowledgeable. She will make sure you understand everything you learn, and she will repeat the learning progress in the class to help you master the knowledge practically important at a dental office. The course is easy to learn, and you will get plenty of time to study for your test. I have two coworkers graduated from West coast College of Dental Assisting and they are on top of dental work in the back office. Highly recommend to anyone who wants to become an outstanding dental assistant!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dhay Al-rubaiawi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeVI_2bxlSd0u4wdG9cOK-4VupCenTIKAbWmiY8eDTSvJq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience at West Coast College of Dental Assisting. The program was incredibly comprehensive, offering a great mix of hands-on practice and classroom learning. The instructors were knowledgeable and genuinely cared about our success, always available for questions and guidance. The facilities were modern and well-equipped, which really helped me feel prepared for my career. I’m so grateful for the training I received and would highly recommend this college to anyone interested in becoming a dental assistant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chelan O’Hare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVcRQ5hBlU3ouLiYbabxQBCBVpMieQBRGudX4d6APt2WeEluc4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"West coast was one of the greatest experiences/opportunities I’ve ever received to learn, and grow as a person. Alexis was the best teacher, she taught us in a way in which we could all understand, she was patient, kind, honest, considerate, but most importantly compassionate. Learning from her and knowing she actually had dental experience to put into perspective for the rest of us was something that I found very important and helpful. Learning for me is quite a task for me, and quite difficult at times. I know teaching people new things is never that easy, but Alexis sure knows how to do it! I thank her and the school for this opportunity of learning and growth, she made becoming a dental assistant so easy and fun!! Thank you for everything Alexis! You’re the best🩵","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
