e front desk is attentive with a strong attention to detail and makes each patient feel important. I could say more about Susie but I’ll move on to the next person.  Katie (name spelling might be off) but the treatment coordinator or finance person. She’s fantastic, super knowledgeable and friendly. Easy to talk to and not pushy very accommodating. Then there is the assistant and I forgot her name but I will reply to this comment and get it because she’s a big part of me feeling so safe and healed. She’s so comforting but fun at the same time. Very clear and easy to understand. Very comforting nature but definitely knows what she is doing. Could not have felt comfortable fully without her. Then of course the doctor is amazing he had the same qualities as I mentioned with the rest of them. This dental office deserves it’s high rating. I’m hoping most of all that someone with dental anxiety that has had a terrible experience and wants to get a dentist team that can make them feel safe again reads this message and meshes the decision to go here. Because that is who I was. I’m hoping I can find other versions of me and get them here asap so they can get the dental care they need and never be afraid again. Thank you Fox team. Super special thank you to the assistant. I’m so mad I can’t remember your name lol.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jen beverstock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmLd13qzVeuA6JRz5CeYSHT4qvPAGv8juT_5PCvrthJuQY5dEP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Dr. Fox for over 15 years.  He is by far the best dentist I've ever been to; he genuinely cares about his patients.  His office staff is always positive (especially Susie!) and the dental hygienists are so welcoming and gentle.  I especially appreciate that Fox Dental keeps up with the latest technology!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nogoodname","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDNdaF-mm7ZUr05pbEoXiHXp77ycfe7kZ6VoxREhV7m-zxyQQL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sandra is very professional, knowledgeable, and enjoyable to work with. She is very easy to talk to and she is excellent at what she does. She always makes sure that I'm comfortable and fully educated on the health of my teeth, as well as informing me what I should proactively do for preventative care solutions.\n\nI highly recommend this Dental Hygiene office due to the superb quality of their services, and of course, their hospitality.\n\n- Chase","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurie Hatakeda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWzi1x7zvv_aseQIHHEkiSJ9Jlfed9FcY0FGb-6KdQ0M1O7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything at this dental office is well done.  The dentist and dental hygienists are very knowledgeable and do an excellent job. The receptionists are helpful and friendly.  My entire family has come to this office for over 25 years. I highly recommend their services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kiris Silva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDSfIEVBO-1Pxf-L5lTmY3nQJDmr9lQtgLBsERWXHS0045GQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The tec was kind patient and explained things clearly.  Dr fox was, as always, excellent.  I always feel my teeth have received the best care when I leave. The new dentist that checked me was very nice and gentle and carefully answered all my questions. And the young lady that cleaned my teeth did a fantastic job. She was very kind.!!!!!  Great care, great office.!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Manchester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUryXHIpS4bLIpLIfUsgyUcpx6xLcWPI6EkY9LWfkmsp7-T7pu_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient at this clinic for many years.  Every time I visit it's been a very pleasant experience because of the way I am treated here.  The entire staff have been very helpful in helping me keep my teeth in healthy condition for which I can't express enough gratitude.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob Holdeman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_d7itr8k61C6bich0oj5uLwfccysdF_5a-tUdsk3UhjT9d2nt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had Alicia for the first time as my Hygienist. She was great. A gente touch \"sweeping before she mops\". She was a wonderful conversationalist, great attitude, laughed at my jokes, likes to travel. Wonderful person. Thanks Alicia for a fine time, even at the dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"George Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsthNp3x4gxpmMKoN1ILqc9zhw-EnIqOIv3TZQ_0Y4X91NhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone at Fox Dental is very kind and compassionate when it comes to your dental care. They take the time to explain your treatment and answer all your questions and make you feel comfortable. Highly recommend Fox Dental.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
