ons":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Antonio Gumataotao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGlt4tEgH7HNxtA5oMdh9u0aip5NMZZAMkdEmT8cGn2A_UiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Pacific Northwest Smiles for the past two years, and my experience has been nothing but positive. I’ve had the chance to work with nearly everyone in the office, and each person has provided exceptional care. Vanessa has been incredibly helpful coordinating my treatment and handling the financial side, while Mayra and Crystal have taken great care of all my dental work over the years.\nEveryone has played a meaningful role in my journey, and I want to give a special thanks to Dr. Greenhalgh for always being personable and positive throughout my journey. You’ve all provided outstanding care, but the greatest gift has been the confidence I now have in my smile. I truly couldn’t ask for a better team. Thank you all!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Soares","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIffnew-pUoyf2SPbOFQzcaqN1Uoqah9_E3yq8ZDZ6cBTkAZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Greenhalgh, his assistants, and the technician took excellent timely care and paid great attention to detail to update and match an old front tooth crown for me - he really made sure to dial it in as cosmetically as I wanted it. This is the best dental care I have received and much better than when I originally had the crown put in by another dentist. He gave different options and honest feedback and didn’t push anything more or less on me that we didn’t agree was best. I felt I could trust his input and eye. Truly a great experience, would recommend to everyone, and will continue to go here as long as possible.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Dominick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJOwe8o3iLXdZ0SetOEOPuo_e37NAQdLFucCO0GrRALa6R2g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the absolute best experience I could've asked for at this dental office. I got a root canal done this morning by Dr.Greenhalgh, and he was so informative, so kind, and overall he and his assistant had the best bedside manner I have ever seen. I will definitely be back and I will for sure be recommending him to all my friends and family!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rossette Tobias-Barr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKD_fJmKjAX4ICVe51ds1LeepgglzXnTnhVkOFiPzzbJTmRFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been going to Dr Greenhalgh at Pacific NW Smiles since his practice opened in the early 2000. He has performed dental procedures for me, my husband and two kids over the years and the quality and integrity of his work has been exceptional! One thing I missed when we moved to Australia for two and a half years was finding a dentist of the same caliber. Dr Greenhalgh and his team are friendly, approachable and helpful with each and every encounter. I readily recommend his practice to anyone who would ask about a good dentist, I would say he’s not just a good dentist, he is a GREAT one!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf9W7wL3jAjF_taFqL32R6rGMq1to7SfCCLXcMA7XovY9Pycai=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Come here for our annual cleaning and checkup. Valeria does our cleaning and is always insightful and welcoming. She provides good level of professionalism and humor making the visit awesome. Dr. An is also helpful with answering any follow up questions we have had. Scheduling staff is also awesome and flexible with us rescheduling.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ricky Odell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGInmyap6MJmZyFmuG0tNokCaPCHq0H3_Jl01VG_tyjLj4BOgd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very clean, efficient, and professional office. Staff is friendly and stands behind their work. Dr. Greenhalgh is great and always eager to make sure patients are comfortable and happy with his work. I shopped around to several dentists and none of them came close to providing the level of service I get here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darlene baldwin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjUD5if7paUOz2zRsWXaiYGA3PiP_FyxZGaJc935Or_2fh0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pacific NorthWest Smiles is a rare find in Dental Care. Both my adult daughter and mother go here and they both have received the most thoughtful care. The office is calm, from check in, to talking about billing. They treat their clients as equals in decision making and finding a plan that will work best. You can tell they are not about just making money. They really care and that is rare. As someone who comes from a lifetime of customer service work, I cannot recommend them more.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Shinto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-zptGcRN5KFBO6MJKHphKgKSj1Xzu9QE0O2hB-IhCF6yFxLj4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent dentistry practice! I have been going here since I was a kid, and they are always very kind, flexible, and innovative. They’ve been incorporating more to their practice over the years, which makes it very easy to do everything in one place. As someone who’s had Invisalign twice now, once outside of this practice, I prefer the way they go about things.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
