ting":5,"Description":"My first visit today!  Had pain in a broken tooth that was beyond repair.  Very skilled dentist and staff. Quick and comfortable solution for my 65 year old molars. Nice experience. Which is crazy to say considering it was a dental procedure.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQ9bPRZbjMK-umF0VHp852hnYlDFuXvdMNFuJHELJtpxnx8Ww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team at dat dental are all professional, relatable, tell you what you need to hear, and will take care of it. Best dental practice I’ve had the pleasure of working with by a large margin.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Srishti Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAMuOy3HjkgD6_K_YykrA3b0o6-mWOfsfb6AF-MhttdQ9hJ5CEow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m a new patient here, and the entire team made sure my visit went smoothly. They walked me through every step of the process, explained all the details clearly, and patiently answered all my questions. I really appreciate the support from Dr. Carol and the staff, it made the whole experience comfortable and reassuring.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gen Sakura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRZvDRh-sf_W0QGGPAXv6GehqkSLazinN63MqEDLusdUeCNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The clinic was able to put me into a spot a week after I called. When I arrived, the office was clean and nice and the dental assistant worked efficiently so the Dr had enough time to get to work on my fillings.\n\nThe reason for the 2 stars was because I was miscommunicated multiple items that results in costs more than double the original estimate. I was told that I would have fillings done on two teeth and that there would be two other teeth would have sealants done at a different time. I was very surprised when I saw that the OOP costs were double what the quote was because they did work on 4 teeth and did not notify this to me.\n\nWhen I received the quote for the sealants, instead of sealants I was quoted for fillings which are much more costly. Again, maybe there were a few miscommunications since the initial appointment was rushed, but I lost trust in the quotes and treatment plan they communicated to me.\n\nThey were also more than 2x costly than my previous dentist for not much added benefit. If you do plan to go, be sure to get the quote of the work being done prior to them billing you just in case.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jackson Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWepPzCXunyD9JTetAtv6wj24ZEkbRge0g80I84OzlL7MxJ0Os=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient at this dental office for 7 years and have always been impressed with the cleanliness and professionalism of the staff. The team is friendly, helpful, and makes every visit a positive experience. Highly recommend!\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"thuy phan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILG1nGzDhmhUy6Nkc8UuyC__-U2g8olzpybkc0fRAteYmogw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am very disappointed to have come here because they have no conscience. My porcelain crowns are loose, food is getting stuck and causing pain, and I want to have them removed. They told me that removing them would cost 3,000,000 VND for two new crowns. I told them to remove them first because I'm in pain and don't have time; I have to go to work and don't have the money to do it now. Then they said removing them would cost 160,000 VND, which I agreed to. But later they refused to remove them and insisted I pay for new crowns before they would do it. They lost their ethics for money, while I was in pain.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Norma L.C.L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7QlOKxM71ue9ZUlFYyeEUWtbDdzgRDrqqHhx9hDzHoXGIZIEDkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Carroll and her Dental Assistent were very patient and detailed.  The office has modern technology and front desk is always very polite.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
