/a/ACg8ocKdl6JtL8pQ-FIulHzEZ3XpbKniAkMscF7L8i7J7TVLDyZpZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a patient of Dr. Beliy for over 10 years, and I truly can’t recommend this practice enough. Finding a dentist you completely trust is rare, and that’s exactly what I’ve found here.\nThe entire team is consistently professional, kind, and attentive. They take the time to explain procedures, answer questions, and make sure you feel comfortable at every visit. I’ve never felt rushed, and it’s clear they genuinely care about their patients’ long-term dental health rather than just getting you in and out.\nOver the years I’ve had everything from routine cleanings to more involved dental work, and the quality of care has always been excellent.\nWhat stands out most is the level of trust I’ve developed with the whole team of Prodental Family Dentistry over the years. After more than a decade of visits, I wouldn’t consider going anywhere else. If you’re looking for a dentist who is skilled, trustworthy, and truly cares about their patients, this is the place to go.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alena Boyko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEf1btDnOV2KNrA2yfl9FKvPQ_FMolwCPsbNj0__PLDF6wMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr.Val Beliy and their team are fantastic! They’re friendly, professional, and make every visit comfortable. Dr.Val Beliy is skilled, explains everything clearly, and truly cares about my dental health. The office is clean and welcoming. I always leave with a brighter smile! Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nadya Maslova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDFcuPvWEdursw87e9VwAzvFFBYXyQrjBerU5mTByJCm3gKc0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was going to this clinic for 15 years now. I am always satisfied with my dental visits. The staff is very friendly and always helpful. Doctors Val Beliy and Ilya Miloslavskiy always exceed my expectations with their amazing work. Dr. Ilya Miloslavskiy is by far one the greatest prosthodontics out there. After his work I had no pain at all and the healing was so quick and easy. The Hygienist Anna is very attentive to my routine checkups. Dr. Ilya’s team is amazing with even handling difficult cases. Lyuda, the assistant had so much experience and exceeds high level skills. Highly recommended this place if you want friendly staff that care about you and your health.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kirkland Now","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQBEfbpe44TGijCrvDQtzy0F-cfsU86As7Hhr_Exix1Ri43Yk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible service. Constant phone calls, rudeness, and pressure. It company interested in your insurance and money, not in the client or their problems. I do not recommend 🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anita Greben","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKxUV88H7SAvT5LNxN6btFJJCzaw2UullA_1jy4r5fPMNQrvA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m not the person to write reviews, but my experience at this clinic was amazing. I needed a tooth extraction and an implant. I’m extremely anxious to anything like that, but Dr.Ilya made my experience peaceful and comfortable.  I didn’t even feel the tooth extraction and the implant went great ! He did PRF with the implant and it healed up extremely quick. I was very surprised, and recovery went by extremely smooth. I’m honestly so thankful I got to get it done and not worry about it anymore. Highly recommend the Doctors and the team. They are kind, supportive and if your like me who gets a little anxious they got your back and will explain everything and insure your comfortable the whole time. 10/10 experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vladimir Litvin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-KGzxar0ho9sk8JShNuFKygMDhgQe37fB9WxZW5uK1C7X6AO4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent dentist, I highly recommend Dr. Val.  I really appreciate his clinic.\nThe doctor and staff are very kind and professional.  They use new techniques that really work. They sure know how to take care of the pain.  Every filling or crown they have done, it feels like I never had any problems afterwards; no bumps or anything like that. I’m very impressed with the quality of dental work they have done especially for my front teeth. The best dental care I ever experienced!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"O Т T.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0K8cJgceBdty_zWKm7JiCIY_kbz1C9Pw8_cULbRV6CMQA9Kfsgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've been patients at this dental clinic for a long time, and we couldn't be happier with the care we've received from Dr. Val and Dr. Ilya Miloslavsky.  Dr. Val has been our trusted dentist for years. Every visit has been a positive experience thanks to his expertise and the professionalism of his staff. The hygienists and medical assistants are always friendly and welcoming, making each appointment a pleasant one.\nDr. Ilya is also fantastic - he's incredibly gentle and skilled. He introduced me to the latest technology in dental implants, using plasma from blood to aid in the healing process. This innovative approach has made the implant procedure easier and faster, with excellent results.\nOverall, my family and I highly recommend this clinic for their outstanding staff and top-notch care.\nOlesya T.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Velman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpRSkp6EetMqS86GDd2MCsOZuMn2e4IOxYB2yybQzqHiAyZk0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"did not have any complains until yesterday when I got a cancellation text message notifying me that hygienist will be out of office on the day of my appointment and that I have to reschedule it (cleanign service). When I called I was offered the next available appointment in two months what is disrespectful on my opinion and the business transferred their own problems on me as a customer thinking I would accept it by default. Considering other clinic now to move to for the dentist service. I see the business lost the customer service level and put themself above the customer what is unacceptable to me. Keep this in mind that your appointment can be cancelled and you will be kicked off the list and moved in the end of queue.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
