hly recommend to anyone who is searching for a dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurie Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRO3oYdUcbGLi7aZ1DQZarAFhZDIrjPxBZqRlGWPqx54-dXR8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hadnt been to the dentist since Covid. It was the perfect excuse. I switched to this office and had a really great experience. They are accommodating and understand dental fears.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
