":"Meagan Troxell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2qecMKnbkhEBgnr3BY5GqYL8eQYVypD9UEaM32Bf0GP-aVw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love this place! The front desk is so friendly, the dental assistant was wonderful, and the doctor who did my cavity was amazing. Everyone is incredibly kind, gentle, and makes sure you’re well taken care of. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gulled Mohamud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw3dJXbUh1mB71RvKvmHs8VZuoSLZtNzlc88lCDy5mo75854w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional Experience at Alderwood Dentistry with Dr. Lam\n\nFrom the moment I walked into Alderwood Dentistry, I felt welcomed and genuinely cared for. The front desk staff is friendly, efficient, and always willing to help with scheduling and insurance questions. The office is spotless, modern, and very comfortable—using the latest technology to make everything smooth and transparent.\n\nThe  assistants are gentle, professional, and attentive. They explain everything clearly and make sure you're comfortable throughout your visit. And Dr. Lam is simply the best—kind, patient, and incredibly skilled. She takes her time to answer questions and never makes you feel rushed. Her calm and gentle approach completely puts you at ease, even during more involved procedures.\n\nWhat truly sets this office apart is how much they care. They follow up after appointments, remember personal details, and make you feel like more than just a name on a chart. If you're looking for a dental office that’s not only professional but also kind and caring, I highly recommend Dr. Lam and the entire team at Alderwood Dentistry","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JD Dryden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVU4RWOjQWA8Cpl5U46vepADEjUWPT6RwSAhPAwzYfS1__-MlUFeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down one of the best dentist, Dr. Lam is wonderful and makes sure you are comfortable and takes care of you right. Her crew is wonderful as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adrianna Goff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrdBZddlODHcgfHwnrOt3xx4RtTXZxDfiaAuncy7zyMzYU8i1M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at Alderwood Dentistry! Dr. Vulpoi and Melanie were fantastic,  they took the time to thoroughly explain each step of my cleaning, as well as the results and follow-up care. When it came to scheduling and navigating some insurance questions, Jenny and Svetlana were incredibly helpful and patient. I'm thrilled to have established care and would highly recommend them to everyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Curulla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVyNI9qYDU0azpAyT5tc_qa6Tr_02IN9d5h7noxKfoqIoDwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff and doctor were wonderful.  They were right on time for my appointment, very professional and kind. I see myself as a patient with them for many years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheryl Marks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbbBPASalYbvv8CZNKDvaFnQsVzq5vKsom4s4PjyK6KpvICBEOVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I normally don't like dentist appointments. I know that I have to go to the dentist. Alderwood Dentistry is very welcoming and nice staff. I'm happy with finding a dentist I feel secure and am able to have excellent care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chessie Snider","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpj5auWOtMFoK9CdoVzThhhPXcTUmEGODMzMofZc_Vj-HEZVkS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The clinic and office feels like a cozy home. The front desk is friendly, organized, and efficient. Dr. Vulpoi is gentle, kind, and takes  my anxiety away because she is so careful. She describes what is going on through stories and metaphor. The hygienist is easy to chat to which helps keep my mind off of procedures. I never feel guilty after leaving an appointment, just knowing what I need to do next. I trust here and refer people here every chance I get, even my own mom. Video of friendly roses out front","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Rz60u28xgbwUCUHDPRmojAqMUJToKVMI-Ar9KXPsT6C8BA8lgTUgTg_DLZb9ShZSea_4_MApyjkzdLZDchs4YlwuHswOaiZ4nveag9rbmp3U765DHUG3ywhYnICuwwgmEF_eeoQ=k-no"],"When":"2022-11-10"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
