lity","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jieyun Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUscQ6cGMDFmXmH1SUNA80cScxGSDDFR3s5aCPqREeRjYYHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Do not question the bill they sent you, otherwise you will receive various excuses in a harsh tone, or even a notice terminating your service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIr16XYjOSHr6rRvkKIhZFGM3NquGnHHV7-EXYn3yRm_QE9hg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Herbison is probably the best dentist I have ever had and I've had at least a dozen.  I saw him many years ago after a previous dentist tried to do an implant and failed miserably.  He found the problem (and other mistakes from previous dentists) and encouraged me to get it fixed.  He did the responsible thing and referred me to an oral surgeon because he cared more about me getting the best treatment than trying to get money out of me and trying to do it himself.  I took his advice and now have a great implant and a well matched crown that he put in.  Other dentists have actually commented how well it was done.  He never pushed me to do anything more than to take good care of my teeth and to monitor anything that looked concerning.  After many years with him, my teeth were in good shape.  Sadly, I had to move and can't find another diamond like him.  I highly recommend him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kathleen Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIM9xydiOh2sapaP5BtnTwMLFz4tghQNTUyXtN5FcHsF0FONQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been here with both of my children (ages 4 and 2) and had a great experience. The Dentist is knowledgeable, the receptionist is very friendly and competent, the hygienist was more than accommodating for my sensitive teeth, and my kids had a good experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"nick murray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULptTXUzPM42cCcAo-TgIi6QMwrH7YZAw43P7G_EkL2dVCl8J6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic practice / team.  I'm generally uncomfortable at dentists but the team was great, took their time, and made sure I was comfortable throughout the process.  11/10 would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQEkUU4rvOrsOHqwA5orisQIH1wP9X5VpX1le6G5Li8a30U5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Misleading should put hours when available to not waste time calling if it’s past normal  business hours.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Casey Herrick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6_JdWNKG7aDfywblDuRLHl2gIWOhlD69WyFYZi6Ks0H1bK3HP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Im not one to write reviews, but this place is great. I have severe anxiety surrounding the dentist, and they do everything they can to make the experience feel safe and keep you informed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"T D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZJr0OKKpiL4c_BDaQY2bM9QbiBW5P7j8Z_8iyYt67KL4tVBU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice people here