rst visit every one following has been amazing, It's like I really can't wait to get there knowing that the treatment I receive will alway's be top shelf from the time I walk in until I walk back out, it's gotten to the point that I'm going to miss my newly found family, when the work is done and I get to the point of annual visits I may have to stop by just to say hi! Every person at Cottage Lake Family Dentistry from the Front Desk to Dr's and Tech's are the best!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaMjIXifkjYzKHoLFaxVrmbRv1AjOAJF8cmLkdZgWIOuL7iA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"On vacation from Canada and needed a dentist. Grandson had a tooth ache on Xmas day that did not go away. Dropped by on the 26th and they were able to fit us in without an appointment. Staff were fantastic and the dentist was excellent. Problem solved and a happy kid. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charlie Barger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFojkhDM_hLj8VF8f_ubb7toNvu3Q4y2SBIpLZGyzh5bRWtSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a wonderful place for dental care. The team of professionals are knowledgeable, friendly and excellent at taking care of their patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aubree Cooper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDesjRR1mUhCmtzahGiNRCndv9LSRRuwwatqwx_mQYrDVCdmCUOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My husband, kids and I went to this dentist for years and have had nothing but problems. Fillings have gone bad, and several have fallen out that they have put in and needed to be replaced. And they make you pay to replace the fillings, even though they were not put in well or correctly. In all my years Ive never had a filling fall out or go bad in under a year or two and in our large family we had several.  We finally left cause they kept charging us to replace the fillings that fell out. And we’re still having so many issues with previous filling done there falling out or failing.  And management was no help! Stay far away from this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Noel Kjosness","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJao1oCst3fCiYyn6Z3PUcCCFNIX6JVCMSWNaG3SsQAzlZgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a great dental appointment!  I love Miriam...she is the best.  The front desk ladies work so hard to get me in for an appointment because I come from so far away.  I travel for over six hours (to \u0026 from) to visit Cottage Lake.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexa P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvZQitSWNptnhkVdKTfNi84LwV7MOoyPPPPN_alPAUN108ZVsd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went to see a doctor because of sensitivity in my tooth. The doctor said it would be better to put a crown instead of the feeling I had. On the day they put in the crown, they removed the old filling and noticed there was an infection. They cleaned the infection, they put the crown. However, it didn’t help with my sensitivity. I went back to the clinic, but they told me the infection had gone down. Now, I have to get a root canal.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
