rough it all","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1MtfcmhGZ7JZvAsUY6uFK0fL4MggNReVxSfspDyUMcaltHl4cSAxugvfND7xQdoSgu_zGhvM4IVJrMe1MC8QzdlETE9AsXwg8m6vK0xP7SgiUQS-QhCHyZQ47Eoy_JohclFn7ln4P6igYn=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1kh16p6c0xDN6MJmHf2UNjhcDLlUzS7p1qIwnv_xPNo7m0rHyatlvjBfkOkm8sa39fWkhJiiwek7Kuls_RXH8LYWvvkifxzDb07tzkXgcYuo8Mfzdt8U9fdq07Ekkm3U9--fkRNQ1uTCzq=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn08fN6L_QBY_U8LeOtCOD8GMtfZw7gkDct8PwM2PyYHEG6JAOJFQ5SIAg8ysQXEWMrJGLi6qLTomraoSs8kwvbOdnhJgh6jKED6IOTa-isHmPV0NQAFax6bheNF-30EVYykdDj3Cq_JtsyD=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-24"},{"Name":"Corey Phelps","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxxcqnxBnqFHo2kwcc61mYWsA4HSKQ_Z_qawFQMm-pnr8d49bh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great team with lots of customer service skills.  Fast, friendly and the  dental care is spot on.  For someone thats really cautious like myself, all my concerns were met.  I can be difficult when it comes to my smile and appearance, but it was no problem for this team.  They even went as far as having a specialist meet with me to assure my new crown would match the existing color of my teeth.  They could of easily just sent out the work to be completed off site, but they went the extra mile and had it done by a specialist in house.  This extra step left me feeling confident about the upcoming work needed.\n\nIn addition, the communication from Jake in scheduling is far outside the norm.  I get answers back quickly and they have no problem working around my work schedule.\n\nIf youre on the fence about going to a dentist, this location is where you should go.  Give it a try and you too will become a loyal customer.\n\nGreat job to the ENTIRE staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dana Yost","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7tOiDLUbRylRJYVHszbxLVR1_io2qzzZ7k03oEOIimhVnZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A quality dental group. Always a good experience. I have had everything from cleaning to filling to dental implant. They are very competent. They are confident and great at their job. The staff is kind and providers have a great bed side manner. I really appreciate going to the dentist with the utmost confidence.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelby M. Crockett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWGxOfAmBNSjW7ymZYGybm6URMyLMjfgajejiZ_dC7QU-nmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an incredible experience it has been to be a patient at Mill Creek Family Dentistry. From the beginning stage of scheduling an appointment over the phone all the way to having my treatment plans continued. Such an amazing staff and team who are collectively the most kind and thoughtful group of people, not to mention they do phenomenal work. I cannot sing their praises more highly for the absolute gift and delight it has been. Not only did they enhance my smile, but they have enhanced my experience at the dentist as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marilynn Crawford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpgrC-mhNc66HgR2E9EVgp9MJkgNfR4hn3QjqtxgUlJUIbCi0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very relaxed atmosphere. Always makes you comfortable especially at the dentist. The dentist and his staff are extremely friendly, professional and again a very relaxed atmosphere . Thank you Dr Tice, Jake and Staff","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittney Pfeifer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWu_KTLi17QIFuSg001lrvwxyr10nvUiQB0rYYI25uO2HFkBRFc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is absolutely wonderful. The dental hygienists are incredibly kind and always go out of their way to make each visit as comfortable as possible. I appreciate how Dr. Tice remembers my preferences without even having to ask. As someone with deep-rooted dental anxiety, I can’t recommend this team enough — they’ve truly changed how I feel about going to the dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anatoliy marushchak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRe2svF_bwukkBkB8m6cCUEWrOAdrBWXlhS-06SvTP5a9JXA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife Lyubov has visited your clinic and had a wonderful experience. Everyone was very respectful and professional and did an exceptional job on her teeth. The assistant was  very compassionate as my wife is very sensitive to dental work. The job done by the dentist Casey Culberson was very nicely done and you cannot even tell the crown or cosmetically done filling on her front teeth from her real teeth. Very pleased with the experience.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
