e.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjP9MUeQqrNoKUwxcdQc4gBGmP5dCfeliDT4s62ju2cpn7HExZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Flew 3000 miles to see Dr Sung for a root canal. Why? Because I trust his work. He's the best dentist in the Pacific Northwest.\n\nIf you have dental issues and other dentists can't figure it out, you need to call Dr Sung. Read my other reviews, I don't mess around. He's that good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dane Dorsey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkyMjMNC3Qa0WmQdk3k2i_6rWoN62hxmdC8UPtugIMpFeILQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just switched to this dental office and was very pleased with Dr. and assistant with cleaning and treatment.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
