 was where we wanted my daughter to get her treatment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ladina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUSGrmF9RE290zevzbpTV-b_cKqql9e6h8SzPzGH0bcqrAz5hz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you for the kind and positive attitudes from the Dr and assistant, hygienist. I will be recommending your office. :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rebekah Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhLIMNA2aJm1txBGg6uneQPyLqdhIaRmC_ZrnWvAQy9Kj95w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love the experience and care Dr. Tsen provides. He is always so detailed and thoughtful in explaining every step of the way what he is doing. He listens and is always patient in answering any questions. He's kind, professional and outstanding in dental care. The entire team is always so warm and welcoming and also very professional. Feeling really grateful for all the staff here. Brenda\nCira and Karen at the front desk. Appreciate each of you and your commitment to providing kind and professional service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Van Valkenburgh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_6376vRPUbaP0Ooi8V9dWis458PhiC1iZfswi_pR5MmYAKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As pain free as one could ever expect. In and out quickly, efficiently and proficiently.\nSera is the definition of cheerful, bordering on bubbly. ;-)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandeep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGvVH-8_Rvv8iMKfweCtJPUv25mQYcEGvSoxFR83NAtMu9GQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Very unethical. They were not clear about billing and charges. They sent a bill to collections and even started adding interest, even though it wasn’t our fault. The quality of service also got worse. We have moved away from Gentle Dental.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
