mended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Addie Picou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXFar2MQ0SurNoKPGT6WW9_i717kT4RTDoAHbMuYsv6baqlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The lobby is beautiful and welcoming, which immediately made the visit feel comfortable instead of stressful. The staff was incredibly friendly from the moment I walked in.\n\nEnrique was extremely gentle, patient, and very informative throughout the whole appointment. He took the time to explain what he was doing and gave helpful tips without making anything feel rushed. You can tell he really cares about doing a thorough job and making patients feel at ease.\n\nBig thank you to Cole, the insurance coordinator, for recommending that I come here. It ended up being one of the best dental experiences I’ve had. I’m really glad I found this office and will definitely be back soon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"O\u0026T Boyko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhCmzZyvvldmG60WcxMfjBS92GjtH6ywvRaBs9PpDBw9OZIhV-FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"had an amazing experience at the dental office today! Dr. Choi and Alisa, the hygienist, were both fantastic. The entire team was so welcoming, and Dr. Choi was incredibly thorough and patient, while Alisa made sure I was comfortable every step of the way. I really appreciated their care and attention to detail. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DLaina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_GC5wc2lyTOLFWU4ukrF3-3YJHFjwW1znkrlHIle6GpyDX1oyNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My three year old son and I became new patients of Kirkland Family Dentistry. I was thoroughly impressed by both of our visits. They were so patient with him - showing him every piece of equipment. All of the staff was professional and kind. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Ciceu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKcnmwfTTreDXTN0T16yaO-B-a2wc1b1CnV_7ZaQKUj3uWp7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough good things about Kirkland Family Dentistry. From the moment I called, they got me in fast when I really needed help, which alone meant the world to me. The entire team was incredibly kind, professional, and reassuring.\n\nThey took care of my multiple cavities, walked me through everything clearly, and even prepared me for a same-day root canal, making sure I felt comfortable and at ease the entire time. Dental visits can be stressful, but they genuinely made this experience as calm and pain-free as possible.\n\nWhat truly sets them apart is their compassion—they went above and beyond to help me with a payment plan, since I didn’t have insurance. That level of understanding and support is rare and deeply appreciated.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dental office that is skilled, efficient, and truly cares about their patients, I highly recommend Kirkland Family Dentistry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJQgCGl61LBVsKWl1aFGaGO9ZgJc57Bs_6ZvONt8caPhULdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a great experience. I had an emergency root canal done the same day I called. They followed that up with a cleaning on my next visit. They were all very nice and gentle. They are my new dentist for sure moving forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lee Liam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrim4T5y-T-9GHby4pXXfaZwZKdUBLn-m-oCBYboAhCA1Epgg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jennifer was incredibly kind and thoughtful throughout my visit.\nSince I’m not very comfortable with English, having someone who speaks Korean was extremely helpful, and I truly appreciate it.\nShe genuinely cares about patients and is very considerate.\nEven though I asked many questions, she answered everything patiently and gently, and made sure to guide me through every part of my treatment.\nThank you again for your kindness and support.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4LlSISovjY0S6HMEdMeCU5CVDkCHV9JHdWheHHWsIwz6aMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Choi \u0026 Amy was great. He’s done my wisdom teeth extraction, it was very quick and painless. Amy shown great hospitality, comfort, and communication. It was my first time there and both of them did an amazing job. This will definitely be my primary dentist","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ali F.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3jL-b9uxUcvAgzwS-MMkDeMqPkryK6wGGl0PCfLrF6cu78g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Decided to change my dental office due to the issue I experienced with this practice.\nLast year, my insurance benefits were fully used without reserving any coverage for routine cleaning at first month of the year. I was uncomfortable with the approach of maximizing insurance usage without considering preventive care. As a result, I no longer feel confident continuing my care with thi office.\nEven I informed them abiut my cincern and they prefer to ignore it.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
