"102615767583867914125","name":"Clearview Family Dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102615767583867914125"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"18122 WA-9 Suite C","city":"Snohomish","postal_code":"98296","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Allan Wattimena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVu0ECTD1AAR0wk4LgsllefS0sPG3Mk1cg52wJegsVIKjlQhu11iA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When a filling from another dentist unexpectedly fell out of my five-year-old daughter’s tooth, I was anxious—not just about getting it fixed quickly, but about how my daughter would handle it. She's little, sensitive, and like many kids, a bit nervous around doctors. But from the moment we walked into Dr. Israel’s office, I felt like we were in the right place.\n\nThe front office staff greeted us so warmly it felt like they already knew us. Everyone—from the reception to the back—was in sync, moving with the kind of quiet coordination you only see in really well-run places. Nothing felt rushed. Nothing felt overlooked. My daughter was treated not just as a patient, but as a person.\n\nDr. Israel was remarkable. Calm, gentle, and incredibly patient. He spoke to my daughter with such kindness and ease that she felt at ease in the chair. No nitrous. No drama. Just trust. She came out smiling, proud of herself. The prize at the end was a great bonus.\n\nThis was more than just a dental appointment, Dr. Israel and her team didn’t just fix a filling; they built confidence. And for that, I’m deeply grateful.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ZpI61Ma4XAt4MfbmDQ9yiU9NzQbI07dDCbs5Nq6gfnIqRyRh2VcaNdJRLfLFA0XiBl0IvNgmui3Y5eMUSFUWLJvKyC41kw_dN8oFmrz0hpV_fTPqQVg_EUHNKDfJWkckkONN21WcTCaQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-5"},{"Name":"Sara M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVreej8jVvZAV5LRtiL2StSxiu69KyatoqPLHrfjJlRkEN8U0PY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Clearview Family Dentistry was truly amazing. I came in feeling really anxious, and the entire team immediately made me feel comfortable and taken care of. Everyone I interacted with was professional, kind, and patient, and they explained everything clearly without making me feel judged at all. My first visit was genuinely easy, and I’m actually looking forward to getting started on my treatment plan and getting my dental health back on track. Thank you to this wonderful team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvsOMbiNjMHFw_sYAWHewypT9FNVYTkqeQZz4LM0k97fzwn0-lZA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team at Clearview Family Dentistry has made every one of my visits a great experience! Between making me feel comfortable during my visits and providing great advice, I'm 100% confident my teeth and gums are in good hands. I couldn't recommend this place enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFZWZ27uWYko8Px7mb7GUHI30eV4aeggr3B9pgJWN4S8Wwpu0B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came to the office with anxiety.  The staff and Dr Israel took time to listen and directly address my discomfort.   After a filling and a crown prep,  I left with teeth repaired and a good plan going forward.  I appreciated their new digital photography showing before and after pictures.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marjorie Njaa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-hODaFVe6130VgSc3m0sCzy-E_g6kRtrqTeryviVkyQFXqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Clearview Family Dentistry! They are lovely people, so gentle and caring. I actually look forward to seeing Michelle and Dr. Israel! They are very professional and did a great job fixing the mistakes of a previous dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nate Schoot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKyw-Q7KeyeAfzRL0KDUb1p7H1j1q8u_ZFbOO2-FOZ_L84xtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful - I have been searching for a practice like this since my childhood dentist retired 10 years ago. They are professional and provided amazing services and consultations. Highly recommend Michelle as well!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Selmer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJdir4QwdfAUd9VFEwPRE91-5KdIVTDruPXOtIOUwvf7QuGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alicia cleaned my teeth so nicely and gently. She is funny and personable and always does a great job. Dr Israel was incredibly thorough with my exam and listened to my concerns","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashleigh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIURcMa9cAbi1QQCkNcDXjJkVRdqqLoV50ar_NYvEGjyndgsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always put off going to the dentist,  but this office has made it a great experience both times I’ve been. They’re honest, never pushy, and really understanding if you’ve waited too long between visits.\n\nAlicia did my cleaning today and was absolutely amazing — one of the best I’ve had. The whole team is thorough, kind, and helpful with insurance and scheduling. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
