/v1/thumbnail?panoid=rhRayiJG_jU2L_H2k-haKQ\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=16.538643\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://www.online-chat.io/crisafullidental","source":"online-chat.io"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"109113779757685945514","name":"Crisafulli Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109113779757685945514"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"18920 Bothell Way NE Suite 200","city":"Bothell","postal_code":"98011","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Paula Proffitt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZoW8u11QW2e_pdiXVkA4aKb_C-agfx9_w-0ikcPIHKchAuFH3Fw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Laos and your staff are great. They made me as comfortable as possible. They took time to explain procedures and billing. I’ve been a patient for many years and find that the high quality of service is being carried on by Dr. Laos.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dzmitry Shalamitski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb3N6IsVySsaIqW4pReiaIAvvaype8FG8d4bqScT0VdJf14FYP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience!From the moment I walked in I was greeted with a friendly smile. Everyone in the office is extremely friendly and pleasant.I must say I was impressed with my dental cleaning and exam. The dental Hygenist Kaylin was very thorough and professional, she took her time to do a great job on my teeth and she gave me quite a few useful tips that I’ll be utilizing in my regular dental routine. Dr Crisafulli was great as well, I have had very brief dental exams in the past but this one was quite extensive and detailed. I could tell she has a lot of experience and she cares about her patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ilona Galenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTc5hIdWc9rJQ47Puy3vx3hWz3OhpfgXP2d6aDtaxBMzdsVTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So thorough. Explain to me in ways that nobody else has. I got products. I’ve been looking for for years to help my teeth be healthy longer.. Doctor, explain to me about pH balance in the mouth. My teeth feel really clean. Great experience","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelly Pierre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLH7cwUznoA16WfnIVDNVv5eHAKbr5TBj0uOgDe21KKZZSahA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dentists and hygienists were amazing and would have given 5 stars had it not been for a billing issue. Office admin mentioned that my insurance billed improperly (in-network vs out of network) and that I owed a $330 balance. She also said it was my problem and that I had to deal with it. I got very upset and canceled my future appointment. After being on the phone with insurance for an hr bc they kept having to call and verify information with dentist office (admin supposedly kept putting my insurance agent on hold), the dentist office had to resubmit the claim or some kind of paperwork and actually owed me $20. I wasn’t going to write this review but noticed the wonderful admin left me a VM and stated how I behaved inappropriately and that she hopes that in the future, I look at things differently.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sophia Ziegler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxCHZun1qx5dQEYy5ARta4OI5DcTTGtQ_fi900O8nSd8BQiSWi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience! Dr. C was super nice, and Kalin did a great cleaning! Marie was very helpful with insurance and billing. Definitely recommend coming here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sanil Pillay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkr_MF34fq9dnxutk8f8z0r-H8P-T_6Q7DpsI7OJxRgU_vuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Houser is incredibly knowledgeable in dentistry, she’s been my dentist for over 7+ years. She’s patient, honest and genuinely cares about her patients care. Office staff is kind and very professional!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aishwarya Bhatt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKbOmG7q7bXy9Yd25Ukx0vF-GMBS7-6El-7_QRB006WuCb8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had one of the most upsetting and humiliating experiences at Crisafulli Dental and feel compelled to share my experience so others can be informed.\n\nI had an appointment just before flying out for an extended time and politely asked the hygienist if my cleaning could be completed in one visit. She declined, which I respected, but I asked that only the services covered by my insurance be performed. At that point, the receptionist Marie was called in — and the situation became shockingly unprofessional.\n\nWhen I asked how much I would need to pay out-of-pocket for the day’s appointment, Marie immediately said \"$500\" without any clear breakdown. When I asked how much my insurance was covering, she refused to provide a clear answer and vaguely said “80%,” avoiding my actual question. I was just trying to understand the cost — which is every patient's right.\n\nMy husband then stepped in to help clarify the situation. When he asked how much we had to pay out-of-pocket, Marie changed her number from $500 to $350. When he asked if that amount was with or without insurance, she hesitated and said, \"Let me see.\" Moments later, she returned with a new number — $180. This constant shifting of figures without explanation was incredibly confusing and unprofessional.\n\nInstead of helping, Marie became rude and aggressive. She started raising her voice and even said things like \"why are you here if you don’t want to pay?\" and \"you could die very soon if you don’t do this today\" — using fear and threats to pressure me into treatment. I was shocked. When I asked to do part of the treatment now and the rest later, she continued to speak disrespectfully and even told me to leave the clinic, saying she’s \"detaining me from the practice\" like she owned the place.\n\nIt honestly seemed like she was far more concerned about her pocket than my health. Her attitude made it clear that compassion and patient care were not her priorities.\n\nI left feeling disrespected, threatened, and humiliated. I have never been treated like this at any medical or dental facility. The way I was spoken to — simply for asking about what my insurance covers — was completely unacceptable.\n\nI do not recommend this dental office to anyone who expects basic respect, transparency, or professionalism. If you ask questions or want to understand your insurance coverage, be prepared to be spoken down to, scared, and treated poorly — especially by Marie, who even went so far as to say, \"Get out of the dentistry.\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kirk Klitzke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwz8-n-oU29vVqyTOTOmDFACLXoiEHGyz96TlRWxNssipE6Z8c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been with Dr Crisafulli for 25 years. I cant say enough about her and the office in general. They have always taken care of my soft teeth and gone the extra mile to help keep them. The only thing better would be if it was free !! Hint Hint ;)","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
