e best dentistry office I’ve ever visited. The staff is always friendly and inviting, the office is spotless, scheduling is the very flexible and pricing is very competitive.\nDr. Aflatooni does incredible work. He takes the time to listen to your concerns and addresses all of them.     He \u0026 his staff are very knowledgeable about new technologies and products and always willing to share that knowledge.... you will leave the office smarter.\nWhat I like most about this office is that the staff remembers your name and all the stories you share with them. They actually take the time to get to know you and your situations to make that interpersonal relationship.\nI highly recommend this dental office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaylyn Germ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZCbFhsQszet835uNV731VU48jU6Z45uTbavzHYZP4NfEZ3z4a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have gone to Advanced Dental Care for a few years now. We really like Dr. Aflatooni and his staff. They are always very professional and personable and they make it a pleasant experience. We have never felt like we drop a ton of money every time we go...which we have certainly felt going other places. They are great at keeping everything very clean and safe, and have always done quality dental work for us.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greena George","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeHhWPvtvSgMui7cHv41C4flqZHxSZw8VCBukcR72ONPFhB3rk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going here for over 10 years and they have been fantastic! Teeth are in great shape!\n\nI like Dr Aflatooni doesn’t push services onto me but let’s me know how I should take care of my teeth. He offered guidance when I asked and he was always receptive to my wishes when it came to my dental care!\n\nHis staff is always cheerful and helpful when it comes to rescheduling!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christopher Bingham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM7KP3j3qejlCV_yR9Fu0P-JqRjqs54HSNNEsza0anVuauWPoG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I discovered Dr Aflatooni several years ago. We're in our early 60s and we've both had a wide range of experiences. Dr Aflatooni is by far the best dentist we've ever had. He's very good at telling and showing you what is going on with your teeth, what he would do to fix them, and then being really good at the actual work. There's no one we'd rather go to. His assistant also rises to their high level of competence and care, and so does his staff. I'd give him a plus on the top of any scale.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fawad Siddiqui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZDJSaIqftFhEOIWZAGEMs26VU1Xki3GehDCt_LNDkqXMbEcXMHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I love this clinic for their friendly staff and their cozy environment. Dr Aflatooni is very humorous and informative. He always try to keep us informed about our dental issues and how to prevent them from happening again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Aflatooni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUK5ZXFVBgU3QiIb4bZdlw4LnDBGrji8Tp0ghtbgd6KsniccbE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely the best dental service you can imagine. I’ve personally had a rough time with my teeth over the years. Issues since I was born. Some of the issues were genetic and others diet. Dr. Aflatooni is my cousin. My wife and I live 2 hours drive away in Port Orchard. The excellence of the experience is worth it. The staff, especially Jen are friendly, kind, and knowledgeable. Pain in your teeth is the worst and fear of unknown issues might keep you back from going to a dentist until the problems are 10 times worse. If you need help then visit Dr. Aflatooni.\n\nTeeth cleaning, cavity issues, or more complicated problems can all be addressed with steady hands that are a reflection of the divine. The comfort level is high, the atmosphere is relaxing, the scheduling system is efficient, and the costs are reasonable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anna W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIknXpAz_ua2ygx2GzT9oSBVOCtG1RtZndBEVLsqPG1M-p2sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After missing a few dental checkups over the years I was very nervous about restarting regular check-ups at a new dentist’s office. Dr. Aflatooni, Jen, and Jennifer are all incredibly friendly and courteous. My husband and I felt at ease during our first checkups. When a long term dental issue came up Dr. Aflatooni took the time to explain the potential treatment options and what side effects I could expect in the future. I highly recommend this provider.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
