h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFjqi5rmMPYPSuG_sJEfGKyB0oOUtaj_69-Vsh2k44InywpJW0KhbQgTk3VpbLd-llifec5edu69dmfJeSgrLO9sM7xIdMrx5AiEC8g2eXrmwj1uFaIBjpREoOCM8LS4sSF4L3HYQ=w449-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=8ZbpXAQUmkbhoRkIwLcqLA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=90.58672\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"109517193680805553286","name":"Creekside Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109517193680805553286"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"19214 Bothell Way NE C","city":"Bothell","postal_code":"98011","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Lorena Dinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-JffYvECx45Ovv6aeZfnmbMfqLL2CtKMMWAkWS0MduVmsDTM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Creekside Dental was warmly recommended to me, and I have been very happy with the care. Dr. Moody and the entire staff are friendly, helpful, and very good at their work. Randie has been wonderful helping me with scheduling, billing, and answering questions. Julie has an amazing ability to thoroughly clean my teeth without causing any pain. Lacy and Dr. Moody do a great job keeping my mouth healthy. I have had fillings replaced, new fillings, and a dental crown, all done with great kindness and attention to detail and minimal discomfort. I also appreciate the cleanliness and comfort of the office and the virus precautions taken. I absolutely trust this team to educate and treat me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susana Mojica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4tUdJDRmL9lPJyvZEUgumRNjAZUdHjvmGDZrm_AKDUJkv-fow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After not attending the dentist for a few years, I had a lot of anxiety for my visit. I was greeted by Randie with warmth, was given extremely thorough information, and was put at ease for my care in the administrative aspect of the visit. She’s fantastic and exactly who you want to see as you check in. During my very extensive x-rays with Lacy I was distracted, given very helpful tips, and treated with compassion. She had so many tips/tricks to help me not gag! Dr. Moody was kind, gentle, and didn’t give me any anxiety as many other dentists have. My cleaning by Julie was thorough and I was so impressed at how gentle she was. I normally leave a dentist office with an extremely raw and sore mouth having been poked multiple times. I was so impressed.\nI really appreciated the time and effort everyone took in helping explain my aftercare. I felt seen and valued throughout my entire visit.  I have zero anxiety over going into my scheduled procedures and doing my regular cleanings. I highly recommend this office if you have any anxiety over going to the dentist.\nI’m so happy to have made an appointment as I visited the Ortho next door!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Doll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU42byTBjbTkAsowyV3mXje87Meb7VDSyF-JUcSgDiSCIXdF4Ab5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went in to Creekside Dental today for my first time. Seriously the BEST dental experience I have ever had. The entire team there is fantastic! They work together as a team so well. They explained everything to me in such detail, I knew exactly what was going on and why and what to expect. I've never, ever had that before. I was even given a hot wash cloth after my cleaning for my face and hands. What? Seriously, they are all so sweet and gentle and knowledgeable and caring. I will never go anywhere else ever again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leslie Matthews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnwJhsqPYn1Zhw6BIGfXVIrLnHKSoLg4YNW2QlGSiC04gpl6I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly, the best dentist I've ever been to. It had been years since I had gone to the dentist and Dr. Moody and his entire staff we're nothing but compassionate and understanding. They always go out of their was to make sure I feel comfortable, relaxed, and ensure that I understand everything that my visit entails.\n\nLori, the lovely receptionist always makes sure my treatment plan is up to date and Lacy, the hygienist is so great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Baze Khamneian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRqQ4sjiSHyMCfGE1solwDROJAL0w0RO3zj_n-VvJc4kxbTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had been looking for a new dental office for a few months until a friend recommended Creekside Dental. I actually dropped by the office and got top-notch help right off the bat. Laurie is amazingly organized and efficient. In no time, my paperwork was filled out and she got my insurance information and all my dental records from my previous provider.\n\nMy actual appointment with Dr. Moody went very well. Everyone in the staff is professional and very knowledgeable.\n\nIt's nice to get this level of service after having put up with my previous provider where they were unorganized, would often screw up appointment dates and times, and would often make you wait an extra 20 minutes in the waiting room.\n\nI would highly recommend Creekside Dental to anyone looking for top-notch dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Stephen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4mvy8aHOTFHsuwBLXxIa64YaZW-YKeGbR0U_H5dagkI07dg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had my first dental visit at Dr.Moody’s office and it was a great experience! The staff was welcoming, professional, and the office was clean. They did a thorough exam and cleaning. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Fleege","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIfsZEcbYLdsg9ux15N-4NeY_U-K-rFR2WoPtpXNW3sy6UjBM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Creekside Dental has provided our family’s dental care faithfully since 2012.  Dr. Brian Moody’s staff is friendly and efficient. Randi sets up appointments with coordinated insurance billing , so I am grateful for the best of care and accommodations!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Krisel Andersen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXUYXtLPKLNVXIbBwOlvHdkoOHtLmsoKMXj8gZNWb1fUjxNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff and services at Creekside Dental warrant a trip from Port Townsend to Bothell!!!  I've heard from some friends they hesitate to go to the dentist because they think they'll be \"pushed\" to have procedures they just can't afford at this point.  I explain that Dr. Moody and his staff are very understanding of their patients' financial situations.  I have a chipped crown which will eventually need to be replaced, but it was Dr. Moody's idea to watch it while I save up for the deductible.  This is an amazing, professional, and friendly office!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
