th Dr. Walter. As odd as it sounds it was agreeable experience. I have been a patient here since 1981and have always had a positive encounter with the whole staff. Dr. Walter is wonderful and Mary is my go-to hygienist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJu-kM8zhvxEJqk_Rtkcvo6LwnkvyRLSIB1wggCmvYHy5KAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have been a patient at this dentist  for several decades. I have always felt the dental care was excellent and the clinic a great balance of professionalism, patient care all while creating a welcoming environment.  Over the last year I have seen a decline and shift in the front office. The dental care and patient well being is still quality, however, I am really disappointed in the front desk. The lack of professionalism, knowledge and ability to process billing has decreased. I am hoping this gets back on track since I value the rest of the practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Calvin Rich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK8wJNoTHNVvaDoNO0yG2lTyrzXE8Z3C7SrKr1-QWblj9g1kg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a new patient looking for a new dentistry, Dr. Walter and Sam did an excellent job in providing me dental care. I definitely recommend The Mill Creek Dentist if you need experienced and straight to the point dental care. Thank you Dr Walter.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patti Dodd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLb7uxwDjCa2HwoHMbPNMxJVGsNYCSzCxc7OEdNdEPTHGNY_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience with  Dentist Kim Walter and his staff was very positive. Kelly dental assistant, was so informative and kind. Dentist was also very informative and helped relieve my concerns regarding my teeth. I highly recommend them to family and friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rafael Tovar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAF5mb2r775Vx2LH9W_RdHsEuL9ZktXglWGPRAUq4URczkBQld=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a new patient! Wow!\n\nWhat an amazing experience from start to finish.\n\nFrom booking with a friendly receptionist, to being helped by an amazing assistant, an awesome doctor, and the person who worked on my teeth, everything was great. Big kudos to the whole office crew for making the visit smooth, easy, and stress-free.\n\nI couldn’t have asked for a better experience. Thank you all. Can’t wait for the next appointments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jean Kraft","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKz_YCHfqeHNQobtddErtL0q7_mjYY_I5Ih6c3wyMBR3OyGWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so thankful for dr Chong and his staff. I recently lost a filling in a hard to reach back tooth which necessitated a crown. I was fit in immediately and the crown was done in one sitting with no discomfort.  I have been going to the mill creek dentist for over 40 years and have always been provided with the best care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"V Roy Chetty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIuirpysLg46cTPPgJa9UbSvDR5a6HBicWtjmLrlnXnTPvzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got to offer my review in light of exceptional experiences received today at Mill Creek Dental .office staffs,cleaning performed by Mary, Dental assistant , Dr Hong and front office staffs. I have used few dentists in the past and have had not so good experiences and services without being subjected to unwarranted upsell and fees and prices after the fact.. today was clear. I will recommend strongly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tatenda Mark Chirima","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwZkaFiN0F1Lvol7Cu6E-p9o3XAIQz_DA370BeDSu8GDt3Ug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you The Mill Creek Dentist team for your care! From front office, sterilization tech, dental assistant \u0026 hygienist, everyone was super friendly. Special mention to Dr Chong for your professionalism and friendliness during my multi-day care. I really appreciate how you squeezed in appointments for me, as I was in pain and needed a root canal asap. Thanks again and looking forward to my future visits!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
