for more than 15 years.  They provide excellent quality of care, and address all of our questions and concerns. They are also accommodative with their scheduling, and are open every other Saturday which makes it convenient to take ppointments for the whole family in one visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lina Alkhateeb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqtY_JvELpItR2EU1H7mHBI7WT3GohLcjiaor5Qqwk93ozfOC9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\n\nWe’ve been going to Pear Dental Center as a family, and the experience has been wonderful! The entire staff is friendly, professional, and great with both adults and kids. My husband and I have always felt comfortable, and they make sure we understand every part of our treatment.\n\nOur 7-year-old daughter actually looks forward to her dental visits thanks to how kind and patient the team is with her. They’ve created a welcoming, stress-free environment for families. We couldn’t be happier with the care we receive here!\n\nHighly recommend Pear Dental Center for anyone looking for top-notch dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lamees Alabsi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJk2hc6_0v1uZItlkAuAxHwotB-VhR9fuUUlFduv0lTZwhh6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been to Pearl Dental Center a couple of times now and they’re one of the most professional Dental centers I have been to! Dr. Jazaeri is a very skillful doctor and VERY caring for his patients, he flawlessly removed a root canal for me and followed up with my recovery. His team is also really nice and always very welcoming and warm. Very thankful for them and their delightful vibe.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Moath Sadaqa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXHeKvUwmvF6DXIt3OfSveX5GsB_D7BVb-ly_Tvwnz1fzmkUuK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Jazaeri and his team are very professional, friendly and care about their patients’ comfort, recovery and overall experience.\nMy wife had a root removal recently, and Dr. Jazaeri made it a very smooth process for her. Also their receptionist Melody is very nice and helpful.\nI absolutely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Saja Khasawneh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzugQ716U7s43Q7WjihCMEbCR5XfwGwfhUw-EJuSeqPsABkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I have been patients there for so many years now. Dr Jazaeri is very knowledgeable and professional. He has always been very kind in addressing my dental concerns, explaining various treatment options. He and his staff are amazing. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"edvac1 dave","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrSRb3oMhmLXUn5WqQO3i_0nQOGx1wAtY9vi9RXkYwvvvmeFfY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent care. Dr. Jazaeri does excellent work. The best dentist I've ever been to. The staff is friendly and courteous; always. Definitely five stars !!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheanna Iverson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUKE8fbJWnfiwXJR1z3TOY9Sz-rxgTifmFmMysN76oxIwT64vG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I love Dr. Jazaeri and his team. My husband and I have been patients there for over 10 years and the level of care we receive is exceptional. My kids just recently transitioned over from their Pediatric dentist to Pearl Dental and they are so happy with the change.\n\nMel, at the front desk is always so positive and helpful.  Dr. Jazaeri is an artist in dentistry. His calm and pragmatic demeanor puts you at ease and he doesn't alarm you with issues or subject you to unnecessary procedures. He is thorough and efficient and takes his time with every patient. He has done beautiful work on my family's teeth.\n\nAfter an accident that chipped my two front teeth, he rearranged his schedule to get me in and fix me up. The work he did with my crowns is beautiful and natural and has impressed other dental professionals.  He recently corrected some poor work done on my daughter by another dentist and we are thrilled with the outcome. I trust Dr. J implicitly with the health of my family's teeth. It's obvious he and his team truly care about their patients.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
