owed his recommendation to get Invisalign and its was one of the best decisions I’ve made — my teeth look and feel so much better.\nThe entire staff has always been very hospitable and kind. Overall, it's been  such a positive experience, and I highly recommend this practice!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rajbir Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTyZ4eGNwb1HmdAsroidPUhyPuwXpexLgxKfET3UgsO7y87qA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience with Dr. Punia and the entire dental team! From the moment I walked in, everyone was welcoming and professional. Dr. Punia took the time to explain every step of my treatment, answered all my questions patiently, and made sure I was completely comfortable. The office is clean, modern, and well-organized. You can tell Dr. Punia truly cares about patients’ comfort and long-term dental health. I highly recommend this office to anyone looking for a dentist who combines skill, kindness, and honesty!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Heather S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVouLoayrM1syzqg_P9ftWFnywaWcfTd_YYf9jem9gIHZcZzBM_fg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I avoided the dentist for many years due to anxiety from past experiences.  I started coming here after I broke a crown and had to come in.  Dr. Punia and the rest of the staff has made my many visits as pleasant as possible and I no longer have anxiety about dental care.  I appreciate the compassion and the non judgemental staff here! I will continue to get my care here in future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TalesSwordsman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvy-1HOa8ZmaFZYEdggeFdtOwh29ZYsH19nXjAg_AUdpW7exUO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Never met a better dental office. They work with you and offer payment plans to make it more affordable. Staff is amazing and super sweet and I cannot recommend a place better than this for your dental needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vanesa Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdNTkg4qNPn7tkwt7QHjosjKt8BEimEOP6xzgE9-0JFWlG6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went in today for my new patient exam, the doctor was very thorough and took a lot of time to explain everything. Jay and Rajan at front desk are very welcoming and seem to take a lot of pride in what they do. Megan and Stephanie are amazing at their job along side the doctor making sure the patients are well taken care of. I highly recommend them to everyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"rozena mistretta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRlNuXHSOvLx875fu-3F8LC-EOMkKUlQhw0KXBnPdtTos3qg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for tooth pain and was treated like a human, not just a patient. Staff is super friendly and professional. The work I needed done was done perfectly and painless. Thank you. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Man Simer Jot kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJoLbnL5f_NUWYlCM6neQ1vgStlaHJXWZT1IBj7ZcLIVsFM2A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is very friendly, professional, and welcoming. The dentist explained everything clearly and made me feel comfortable. The office is clean and well organized.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sixersrini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmgNEZ7S8uW2BigmBSQ6ctNejGBPAOYZYokhLv-Gl3_P22Uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Punia did a fantastic job of addressing my dental concerns. The services were timely and the staff are very friendly. The facility has modern equipments and located conveniently in the Mill Creek Town Center.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
