e":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Rosa Cortes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnWtBqm3thwroVIUQ-RxbeW1BUstlBshEfcjLiGXlf6_aP6Ao=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a new patient, I have already been in this office several times: deep cleaning, fillings, and crown. From my first appointment walking into the office, it felt calm, efficient and professional environment. The office staff is always ready to greet and check you in with a smile. The waiting lobby has never been overcrowded, so I have always been seen quickly without feeling rushed during my examination. Dr. Kim and his assistants are professional, and caring. Dr. Kim explained, and answered all my questions, every time and did a great job with a new crown. I have seen both hygienist, Ju and Isaac, and both cleanings were done effectively and with great care. I have changed many times dentists for one reason or another, but Kirkland Cornerstone Dental has, so far, surpassed all my expectations.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Harmon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-UYWy4utOmq5oENiILM7JUpSqPFsIRux5HMUIliXLT9I7og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A short while ago, I decided to change dental clinics and made an appointment, in person, with Cornerstone about 5-1/2 months in advance. Very impressed with Lily who spent a lot of time on the phone Re my new, unique insurance, handing me a form to sign to request films, etc., from previous clinic, and forms to complete and bring in at time of appointment. This morning I called because I had a dental emergency. To my surprise they had two openings today. I thought they must not be that good because of those openings but I was wrong. Dr. Kim was nice, efficient, and dealt with my infection quickly. The whole staff was wonderful, amazingly kind, and the front staff showed me how to use the two bottles of treatment rinse I took home with me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carlos Bayne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJPO50V24DXOyNZj1w2Npn9mVdS7OldDCQ1UPG1ChOnmv2jklD5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First impressions often last - get it? See what I did there? First visit to a dentist after spending the last two years in the desert (Tempe, AZ) The entire staff was welcoming, and awesome. The doctor was compassionate and fun. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharon Saul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZo9iHNywhuUQu3IRYFvEVrBzKhIrCXVUvuJ5EDI6oC-t77g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great first experience. The office staff was very helpful and knew so much about my dental needs. I met with the Periodontist and he, also, was very easy to engage with, very supportive and thoroughly explained my options and what comes next. I walked away feeling very well cared for.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erica Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5pJaYxg2Nfkki6I7KFKa2U4aSvS9yiwoM-sc3S2Sx96291Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first time here! Honestly would give them a million stars. They were all so kind and welcoming! Very clean and fresh environment! Was greeted by each staff member with a smile and very relaxing comfortable vibe! The dental hygienist was gentle and my cleaning feel so nice and refreshing! The dentist was also general and very informative and explained everything in detail! When I was done with the appointment the receptionist was so kind! She printed everything that needs to be completed. It was organized in a layout with what the dentist recommended with the pricing. When everything was explained the receptionist also let me know that we don’t have to go exactly to the plan and we can make changes if needed. I was able to get scheduled for my next appointment when it work best for me! I love that I didn’t feel pressured to schedule. I am looking forward to the continued care at Kirkland Cornerstone Dental! Over and beyond professional!!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheryl Eren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVHHUk7vjyn3xekiHZJJQADotfQ2SQag9e-UjhD7bSLI7wcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Since I moved to the state of Washington in 2016, I've been looking for a good dentist. Yesterday was my first visit to Cornerstone Dental. Now I don't make reference to the dentist I go to, but instead I'm saying, My Dentist. I can't remember the last time I had such a thorough general cleaning. This team has integrity and are their for the patients best interest.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judy Kirwan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI65E8vOLgIe-zsCXekc6sE-6IHvBXSceA3_um8KNDEH9a6yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the atmosphere.   The receptionists were very friendly and helpful with figuring out my insurance.   The technician who took the x-rays  was extremely professional and courteous.   Dr. Tran was patient and understanding regarding my many dental issues and explained procedures very thoroughly.   I've  definitely found my new dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cary Granger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBgsvToLigJ9eT-PTZro8IWFFdZ4FV58xsi3ZZyJePRjN5zg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to this dental office for over 40 years...\nOwnership has changed only 3 times...\nThe new ownership is just as good as the first two, very professional, very knowledgable.\nToday I was moved to teeth cleaning only 2x annually.\nI was at 3x annually, but the hygenist today said my teeth are looking good and now only need to come twice a year.\nVery happy with that news!  :)","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
