on to the office. The office itself is very clean and and comfortable. They truly cater to the needs of their patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mayra Gomez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2pEIlKSOXDk46B7rbzhvv-hjaYRG1jwvwDrUXdNXd6LmNw2-O=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location, and everyone is very nice. They don't upsell their services like my last dentist. Overall, it's a great experience to come into a friendly, honest space.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Casey Germino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEtkUjaWhaJDrNZwWBYGPpywxMOLXo-T0TEaJLNkle2ZbDK85Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Colleen is the best dental hygienist! Super gentle \u0026 thorough~ I always gotta thank her for the tooth massage after my cleanings! Been going here for 8+ years \u0026 continue to go for my cleanings! I always look forward to every visit","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Madhini Nirmal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_iWtE4GW_dB_tr4vMmBXWGN1JpJilQbUqhaIsj6Y51cyptHfj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff explained procedures in detail, and made me feel at ease. They were very kind, clear about costs, and did a great job with the cleaning and assessments. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Razan Habash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIph-PGZQTp7YA5YLYBniWXcXC29XQR3Hz-6Gr3rGXKFgSVow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Karen and Dany were incredibly kind and welcoming. Dr. Karen stood out with her warm personality and great sense of humor, which really helped ease the stress of a dental visit. They thoroughly assess your teeth and clearly outline the priorities, allowing you to make informed decisions without any unexpected surprises. I highly recommend this place!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
