cription":"I have to say that the service efficiency of this clinic is very good, and the doctor will not over-treat. This is my first time to this clinic today, and I received very good service. I raised my questions about my teeth to the doctor, and the doctor patiently answered and gave me conservative solutions. I am very satisfied.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan Kelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTovq364CJ5m4jNVRSHpBQwujfO0-q5gGYPisrce5GEifIOw8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great staff and doctors. Very clean and friendly staff. Will continue to have my dental work done at True Dental in Bothell. Thank you for the great service and hospitality.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Valera Lincoln","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWU7Ku4MuXiiPf_23J9_Vx7qtWrRX8i9qykZ51sfa89gBuo3vo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The VA referred me to Dr. Wang and I couldn’t be happier that they did. He is dedicated and a very good Dentist.I needed that root canal for a long long time. He did not hesitate. The problem was repaired and I’m no longer struggling. I’ve been to several dentists complaining about this. Dr Wang saw and solved the problem right away. I feel lucky. Sometimes it’s hit or miss with dentists. Dr. Wang is outstanding. So is his staff.\nDr Wang also repaired a problem with one of my crowns. I didn’t even know I had a problem there. He submitted for authorization and he fixed it without even asking, no hesitation. He really enjoys being a dentist and I feel safe there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shady Mina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW5-QkolG4GovK8aCfMQjs5tKiugnnlkc7Kh5iPDdHg93TtaGP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recommend trudental, they are really nice \u0026 never had a problem\nI had an appointment next week and something came up so they were able to schedule me for today","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Zd-e6cj2kOZFITidaMKO_yOY9QLxtIMm1vZOuGKY5XiMUKQrUimsAMOtfjS_fMNUMRecPU0x-LBhXrLBJuQaq20LXXBguqVYCYywEFdOTe1vEpx0dRdA0PuaYyHhxZDfoe9g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2n3zqPn2rg4v5AT1ODueuR3lHXoUKNZZCuY-ZkA4dEDzbS0rGqEreiwU-wG9a62e2XZ2gQOUp41AMfuZ2rrZnknzfK1IPxQwuYNZvkHgW5Npfa8Lhd75Hg5Fc7jA8KFk5DFi5Yzw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Kl8Dxk_IodWK-OYYvKF5r7HF7vDkJm1UQC8PrXFQCrwxbYJyJsOfR8XWsGdnOE1ePvb8s3yCUl2Nx7ywRl2Pyt2qHyS-NGjxrP_iSy42G8GuXLjg5qoCKFzfEedqioMtDdr-C=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3vJmx3tbT31JTHTjJ1_pEIcypphzDj8VQQcOt48YypuuJHPtIuMJb-IuXyfhpxVGkvoI5vZmyGIsIl8qziQAvwJDfhNp-NlENlBMVzkePFZqixDdDpwqZ7dsQMqWe6v2nvUIn_mg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Ql5_WQEgwNd3-3h57WKhsGVRfo_pej_fyJv4SevEa4ldpmYBqOPSeDvWFIYl4ZxE00I2dce8DDmPfiWk9yv5_zms5xMv0Tki0BkHKkXvaLs8e9uQ8ZgHugsyicncP9f-kDkE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1umOBz2jajaIg2Bv-OS2Y2lm_ndhc4me_PADoakUQ8fBIjZDEgk2HdL3OUm_lhrqMmq7txTePRzRfmPlCxM3k7ZSDgyUqAdTWhMDIJg4M1eSID5l0UaNgMpOfWJI0cKaRa57wqJA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2JLj4gOKSQc__BHeFkkIap995ZoFcBNabzTGMfh1J7y5pKj1x6r9x7nqTV-yvtfRJG3gSmLXZqUUm51q5yRyeobI8OtixQ4PpMyQARGRbikOFp9qy0SlVNGKxKJSSVWpuFxrI=k-no"],"When":"2022-9-30"},{"Name":"Maathangi Ganesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKU1cM8PAaHiD-XGKwUavNkNNUiNl-jLw5_AezOi73CISwQhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Steve Hwang did my front tooth filling after I had chipped it accidentally. I was super upset about losing my tooth, but after the work by Dr. Hwang, I barely notice any difference compared to before. He was so patient as I explained how my tooth used to look and spent a lot of time getting my tooth nice and perfect. He did an amazing job and I'm grateful to him. Also I have to mention - all the staff including the front desk are very nice and helpful","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDCbMjL30jeWwxDTZWDD1qTqoEx_jLFp1e3bvNNu-Hr4F0-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've known Dr. Steven Hwang for more than 10 years. I am a local orthodontist and he is my dentist. He understands occlusion (how the teeth are supposed to fit together), he is very knowledgeable with TMD (TMJ issues). His techniques and skillsets are absolutely amazing. From diagnosis to treatment, everything he does is absolutely the best. He uses warm composite technique which ensures that the filling is bonded to every part of the tooth. I trust him with my teeth as a fellow dental colleague and he treated many of my own office staff members. Great bedside manner and great work. Keep it up, Steve!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Khaela Testado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOipoyr3fWmMh8gWFGR8QvgIqq91XfA_bKniABjrPIIaaef9IObw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If there’s one place to get your yearly cleaning done this is the place to go! The staff was super kind especially the dental hygienist that cleaned my teeth. She was extremely careful and took note of my sensitivity. She was a delight to be around and made me feel comfortable as the noises from the drill and scaler give me anxiety. 10 out of 10 would recommend. Place is nice and clean and quiet.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
