 to come! My entire family receives excellent care from Dr. Jonnes and his staff. Thank you for all you do!!\nIf you are in need of an excellent dentist please reach out to their office. You will be happy you did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Korinne Peacock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPiTUJYOK7ISEb68ghuJzwKbI8Ngsa4YbnMB_SZ5nTvuKyk61p=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience! On my first visit each person I came into contact with was kind, welcoming and professional. I would absolutely recommend this dentist and team to my friends and family!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C. Perreira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEbyrL9THC94lSsrlyyBqkzRmRk8XrDLuhwfNGvyDJZ8bzUIkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for a second opinion and I am so glad I did. Was so incredibly nervous at first. But dental assistant listened, empathized, answered all my questions and put me at ease. You could really tell that she genuinely cared about helping people. I appreciated that so much. The dentist was equally kind and empathetic. He was very thorough and a good communicator. He answered all my questions and proactively shared helpful information. No one was judgmental about my dental fears. That was a first for me. I am so grateful to the folks in this office for their kindness and competence.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Middleton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKR5Yo3o0LjhaOf20rGkVvFjkTmpAKeSvCaMj9BXhL4kEQLKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great staff, gentle and quick technicians. I’ll come here as long as possible. They’ve always been good to me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOWTSnKjGO-Uld2VXyY9A0A6w1PzUcMegU9mviQSqZKYzgj6fX6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff are amazing and Dr Jonnes listens and explains everything he is doing. If you are nervous to go to the dentist, I highly recommend  Cedar View Dental! ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Ballard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLglMJJZSQ_iYBxvRgc_Ig5PwKQiadUT8HUb_hSVpUR1bG0Uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Taking care of my family’s teeth and gum health is very important to me. Having this team in our corner is 5 stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sea Swan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU08QZh8IGmpUfMioftlWFi2xdLAk7xLxeLVaTDZYXlluxurjsF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to this dental office for about 15 years and Gina has been doing my cleanings all this time!  It doesn’t matter what people leave or new people come they have all been wonderful to me. I would never go anywhere else🥰","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"* sensei * * senpai *","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkLnW55OGkueYXTJp-R5YJxpY4mtA1vOY_jpWciK8CavTaO7wb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staffs are very welcoming and always greet you with a smile. I've only been here twice and my experience has been great every visit! My dentist always put your comfort first and is gentle in all procedures. Looking forward to be staying in this team from this day onward! Team Cedar kodus!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
