"Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marie Armitage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJc-Vd5GCPhoL5f1yi9fioMOGqFUEeEvZAHVIUzoeU7X58mMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My entire family goes to Dr. skiable at Progressive dental group. I’m by my entire family I mean my parents in-law, sister-in-law and her family and my husband. They’re great doctors office. They never make you feel bad for not flossing, They are clear and concise, and I don’t feel like they overcharge us whenever we need work done.\n\nOverall, I highly recommend them for dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diane Swanson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4RsBG-UREFL8D92r5grWnvedbaBCJ_fPhudHo82JXatzQuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a pleasant experience I had going to the dentist!  Heidi was my dental hygienist and she did a wonderful job. She was thorough and knowledgeable and kept me posted as we went along answering any questions I had.  Darlene at the front desk was an absolute angel! She dealt with the whole insurance thing and got me set up with an appointment for an evaluation with another doctor.  It's a real load off my mind to have everything taken care of like that.  What a great team!  Couldn't be happier!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJV5nlOgY3EfBu-uYzrSazzLIxNqMkT7700b-Xj3kLb-ejDUlF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you Progressive Dental for being the most thoughtful \u0026 kind office I’ve been with this group for over 5+ years and love that they remember to check in with me on a personal level. Their facility is always clean, professional \u0026 calming. I personally want to thank Heidi for being caring, connective and compassionate what a blessing it is to have such an incredible supportive team when it comes to my dental health. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Takano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuk37RjwE4VJsz3RgIlUxvJZNVdKmnHUy2OSs9_VuHs140DXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I appreciate all of the friendly, organized, professional staff at Progressive. I've been a patient here on and off for decades. My dental hygienist, Lexi, has been the best! She is welcoming and does a phenomenal job of explaining things, maintaining an easy environment, and cleaning thoroughly and *gently*. Go see Lexi, tell her I say hi and thank me later.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aliya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2wsnaNzK57mj_I0z16E1NLTm24f4w3orcWnCp9yZAqW3Njw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Progressive Dental has been the best choice we have made for our dental health. They are kind and friendly and do not push unnecessary procedures. I came to Progressive from another office. They had to do a lot of repair from a previous dentist. Every time I go I feel welcomed and understood. No one is shaming you or forcing older dental practices ( metal filling or metal crowns). They are even able to do same day crowns which is amazing. We are so grateful to have found them. We are Progressive Dental patients for life. Dr. Berry is terrific! Calm and so patient.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaymee Johnston RN, BSN.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0-i5tnl84amZ-ijA9LuAVtcrEjNz5MksTjhBGidCjfLpyIQfOag=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient at Progressive Dental for many years now and have nothing but the very best experiences with them. This is office does it right, from providing responsive customer service to exceptional and gentle patient care.  The staff at the front desk and everyone I’ve met in the back, have always been kind, helpful and gentle. We have moved several times and currently live a little over a half hour away, and I will happily always make that drive because I know that I am in the best hands once I arrive.  Thank you PDG!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
