MjX1nAwgUg7sTlI0dw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I did a lot research to finally find Dr Kunal, for my implants. The clinic is amazing, the staff made me feel comfortable right away, and I feel like I'm seeing friends, when I have an appointment. It's such a pleasure to go there. Dr Kunal and his team at the front desk, and actually the whole team are exceptional. Dr Kunal is extremely skilled and the whole process was smooth. He takes his time to explain things and I couldn't be happier with the results of my implants and crowns. Thank you Dr Kunal and all the girls at the front desk. You are the best!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"LEE CLARK","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPaLmEc5CSZdfng4LnIMER8AUhZwtjxnvqhO-Ea3KaXBzWifWntQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had not been to the Dental Atelier for quite awhile and yet the familiar\nfriendly faces still managed to remember me from a couple of years ago! The hygienist was wonderful and the cleaning process went extremely well! She was very assuring with what I was doing right with my dental hygiene and made some suggestions as to what I could do better! A very good experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Morgan Johanson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRj9OBsuZSJp8ULEDzKWOQ-eapowWOhj_G41i6Tqd8jI0srw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A fantastic experience!  From the office staff To the dentist providing your care, everyone is top-notch.  The experience of going to the dentist is stressful, but this office is dialed in to the patient's care and comfort.\n\nsincerely,\n\nOne satisfied customer","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"steve scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRnAs8rEbql6Tw2e8HJbkIU2YSYXXhZD5b2FtmbEz5dKKAMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"dental work is never fun but when you need work done and especially implants I highly recommend the Dental Atelier in Lynnwood. The staff is great, and they really know what they are doing and pricing is fair, same or better than the regular dentist, will work with your insurance, and you get a real specialist for great results. I have had 2 implants a year ago and a crown and now I am back for another implant. Very Happy with these guys.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jaywalken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1JbDHb7movomGAoVtae0Vo8xdfWSNLqUJULkIOundu0IVWw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my cleaning done today, \u0026 I can't say enough good things about my hygienist Darian!! She is truly amazing!! The Best!! Also, I wanted to add, the next day I was able to do couple fillings with Dr. Aiman, I could not even tell when he was numbing me/doing the work. He is so gentle \u0026 very precise.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Crissinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7o0A8Yzfxg18jK9XfR5uq-jslvd00SiIiQs4JuY8IBCgpJ4Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team at Dental Atelier were top notch and treated me with respect and care. I was quite nervous about going to the dentist because it had been such a long overdue appointment, but I was treated just as if I had been a client with them already. Thank you! I’m excited to start my dental care and tooth implant journey with Dental Atelier.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Malibu66@gmail.com Chuck66","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe-rl54AoNJ1HQlBtvBx3vGwvol3nojt1HK67ZNvoamGkXsM7x=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The doctor and team are wonderful here!  I've had a lot of work done on my teeth and I can't tell you how good of experience I have had with them. They're great with follow-up,  reasonable prices and explain everything very well.  Very happy with their work and would recommend them to anyone!  Chuck","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nikola Gorman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_M15G2ICCP4uvpCQWzrx35eif3gM-mVlX4mSXHw-hWObeehfuHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The doctors povide pofessional gentle care and staff are friendly and aim to please. Was able to get 2 crowns done in  one appointment before end of year and they worked around me getting sick and had to reschedule. I highly recommend them. Bonus is their close to Alderwood Mall.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
