tic from start to finish and Dr. Lee was personable and efficient. Scheduling was super easy for a follow up appointment also. Thank you to everyone at this office for making dental check ups an enjoyable experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"RJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyBpjU2BQHD8tvLI2vLRRKhnC1-Jj9CJYwYb0DqM-roUdR-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am not a fan of coming to the dentist. But I HIGHLY RECOMMEND A Northwest Dental. From the moment you walk in the staff is very kind a nice. Jennifer was very welcoming, Joseph was very educational when it comes to the financials.\nMy hygienist was Cherie and she was very thorough. Tess was great as well, making me comfortable and helped eased my anxiety and phobia of coming to the dentist.\n\nThanks all!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Wyman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcvCdkN2MzaRGmDPeWgqdMD97ywraMDQlE2ZRGQtfRWcIX8Au-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have not been to the dentist in awhile  and was a bit nervous, but the staff was so friendly and made me feel welcome it definitely eased my fear.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Crockett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSOgDhLDx82AU3iHLUB9sc6xmETcAGDc8XMnSk3WROlTp_NUs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Received and estimate from them and assurance that our insurance would cover a procedure. 2 years AFTER the procedure was done, I received a bill for $500 claiming my insurance did not cover it. What a scam.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carolyn B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmnFWvuXMntdxYSLEJk4OKNA56ldUi7F8k1XCPF2wE4SXkHnBpKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Dr Lee, Jennifer, Lora, and everyone at A Northwest Dental!\n\nThey're fast, thorough, kind, and open later than most (for a dentist!). They always remember me and everyone is always in a good mood. I'm so happy to have found them.\n\nLora is a wonderful hygienist and probably my favorite one I've ever had.\nDr Lee is knowledgeable and he did a great job finishing what a different dentist started (and they did a not-so-great job).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hui Ni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1x5fR8tLKMaLjVCulKttDP3SmyEue3-0OTJY3cazYjpeerw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been visiting Dr. Lee for longer than 20 years.   Dr. Lee's expertise and attention to detail are exceptional.  He always take the time to explain procedures thoroughly. Their hygienist, Laura is warm and thoughtfull.  Plus, the office is modern and well-equipped, creating a comfortable and stress-free environment.  I highly recommend Dr. Lee for anyone seeking professional and reliable dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Valerie Quince","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWA1YGEdiiGosSQiUkaRqP-9_dxu9TA-EQm7_Af2IJ1OMcSoGSP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Where do I start? I have my mother with dementia being treated here because of how tiny she is and these folks have a great reputation with working with little ones! I absolutely love Jennifer and the the \"Rainbow\" sort of staffers who are very kind and flexible. Dr. Lee is amazing with my mother and I drive over an hour to have him care for mom.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1N-CE90xarBhOIRQ0pLJPjB6yE6RxHy25KSryjyXNA47Md90Og5sPN7IVJ2xqBwu5IClckyziNsjf0uTtToByvC3ykcZ3On1GtXrPrkqcZU7qpYt5REy1EawUqtY2EH43MsxPkQr-oKXAO=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2awWymxFReMwgVFPyrk3bvh1A2D6UMoiUooz2jYxpWyzf24eG5DCis2ehMjIHlkXL-MFcxErlV8Z5wS9sKfPteFF4CZ_A7K9IuBSyf5-x0jdlvTJFRQ7QWm55uuAzXN2peH_K1F0-fGJ8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn28ajOKpN0GYDFtBWixJiZ9nx5AMmbIaKgL-r2rnFiR2POZPi7CgbVefkrKcvS3lTeSlpBuSALomjfgjFTUSZBGj2hRvZvt7BJaORe91Gdf3pUwVjCEXBGh